    # s happy "Do not look so surprised. I had much more free time on my hands when I was in middle school." with dissolve
    s happy "No luzcas tan sorprendida. Tenía mucho más tiempo libre en mi haber antes del bachillerato." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:598
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_2b10e09f:

    # "Before, maybe I could have had this conversation with you, Nozomi, and everything would have been great."
    "Antes, tal vez podría haber tenido esta conversación contigo, Nozomi, y todo habría sido grandioso."

