translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_84980f44:

    # k "N-NOZOMI?!" with vpunch
    k "¡¿N-NOZOMI?!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1020
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ade3bece:

    # "The moment I uttered that phrase, Nozomi's eyes fluttered closed and she slumped forward towards me!"
    "¡En el momento en que pronuncié la frase, los ojos de Nozomi se cerraron y ella se desplomó sobre mí!"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1021
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_1279d033:

    # "If I hadn't been standing here to catch her she would've tumbled head first onto the floor."
    "Si no hubiera estado aquí parado para atraparla, se habría caído de cabeza contra el suelo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1023
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_abd72f8c:

    # "What the fuck was she thinking? Goading me into using her sleep trigger like that?"
    "¿En qué carajos estaba pensando? ¿Provocarme para que use su ancla para dormir así?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1031
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_0f4d79dd:

    # "In any case, I manage to move her slumped form over to my couch and set her down as gently as I can."
    "En todo caso, logro mover su cuerpo desplomado hasta el sofá y recostarla tan gentilmente como puedo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1032
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_50a58f17:

    # "She remains seemingly out cold, while I try to calm the heart trying to escape my chest."
    "Luce completamente pacífica, mientras que yo intento calmar el corazón que intenta escapar de mi pecho."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1033
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_0c0f5725:

    # "Like, fuck, I imagined holding her in my arms before..."
    "O sea, carajo, había imaginado sostenerla en mis brazos antes…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1034
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_1151f0a7:

    # "But, uh... I thought it'd be more romantic than this."
    "Pero, eh… pensé que sería más romántico que eso. "

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1035
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_52b5a6f8:

    # "And how did she even manage to drop so deep? We only spent a few minutes teaching her this in trance a couple days back."
    "¿Y cómo consiguió caer tan profundo? Solo pasamos unos cuantos minutos enseñándole esto mientras estaba en trance hace un par de días."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1036
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_67494649:

    # "But... shit, nevermind that for now. I look to her dormant form as my mind races to figure out what I want to say to her."
    "Pero… mierda, olvidaré eso por ahora. La observándola en su durmiente estado, mi mente se acelera, intentando pensar qué le quiero decir."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1037
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3a4350d7:

    # "One thing's for sure, I need answers."
    "Una cosa es segura, necesito respuestas."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1038
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b85cdde5:

    # ks frown "N-now, Nozomi, I'm gonna wake you back up in a moment..."
    ks frown "M-muy bien, Nozomi, voy a despertarte en un momento…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1039
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b98fd5b1:

    # ks "And... and as you wake you'll tell me what's going on with you."
    ks "Y… y al despertar, me dirás lo que sucede contigo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1040
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_79675ca7:

    # ks "Why you wanted me to trigger you just now, and..."
    ks "Por qué quisiste que usara tu ancla, y…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1042
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_09df7a4f:

    # ks "Just... tell me the truth, okay?"
    ks "Solo… dime la verdad, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1043
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_753abe82:

    # ncg sleeptalk "Okay..." with dissolve
    ncg sleeptalk "De acuerdo…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1045
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9f105881:

    # ks neutral "Alright, Nozomi. Waking up on three." with dissolve
    ks neutral "Muy bien, Nozomi. Despierta a las tres." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1046
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_2a6a8f5c:

    # ks "One, two... three."
    ks "Uno, dos… tres."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1048
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e63a51c9:

    # "Nozomi's eyes flicker and open as she draws a long breath, before her gaze falls sadly upon me."
    "Los ojos de Nozomi se abren y ella respira profundo, dirigiendo su triste mirada hacia mí."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1049
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_d6ecbca6:

    # ncg "Kyou, I... what we're doing..."
    ncg "Kyou, Yo… lo que estamos haciendo…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1051
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5e4917c9:

    # ncg drooping sleeptalk blush "It's about more than just hypnosis with me."
    ncg drooping sleeptalk blush "Es más que solo hipnosis para mí."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1052
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a6ecf7a7:

    # ks surprised "What?"
    ks surprised "¿Qué?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1053
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9458ffca:

    # ncg sleepy "Uh-huh... I know it must seem like I have all the power in our arrangement. But that's not how I want it to be." with dissolve
    ncg sleepy "Ajá… Sé que debe parecer que tengo todo el poder en nuestro arreglo. Pero así no es como quiero que sea." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1054
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3a0f4e90:

    # ncg standing sad "And as I just showed you, you actually have a lot of influence over me while I'm in your house." with dissolve
    ncg standing sad "Y tal como acabo de mostrarte, de verdad tienes mucha influencia sobre mí mientras estoy en esta casa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1055
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ba4243c4:

    # ks "Huh? What do you mean, Nozomi? What influence?"
    ks "¿Eh? ¿Qué quieres decir, Nozomi? ¿Qué influencia?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1056
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_34ee8f54:

    # "I mean, all she showed me is that her trigger still works. And that's only because she allows it. We both know that."
    "Digo, todo lo que me mostró es que su ancla sigue funcionando. Y eso es solo porque se lo permite. Eso ambos ya lo sabemos."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1057
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9f7b39ac:

    # "So what influence is she talking about?"
    "Entonces, ¿de qué influencia está hablando?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1058
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_101d525d:

    # ncg neutral "Well... Okay, we both know you can't literally force me into trance and have me accept any suggestion you want. That's crazy." with dissolve
    ncg neutral "Bueno… Está bien, ambos sabemos que no puedes literalmente obligarme a entrar en trance y hacerme aceptar las sugestiones que quieras. Eso sería una locura." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1059
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_79ee3e31:

    # ncg stern_closed "Of course you're not literally controlling my mind..." with dissolve
    ncg stern_closed "Por supuesto que no estás literalmente controlando mi mente…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1061
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_cf4a80a8:

    # ncg drooping sleeptalk "... B-But wouldn't it be fun to pretend you could?"
    ncg drooping sleeptalk "… P-pero ¿no sería divertido fingir que sí puedes?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1062
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_8fa773e7:

    # "... Right. Of course."
    "… Claro. Por supuesto."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1063
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_8ddd3973:

    # "It's not just the thought of being hypnotized that gets her going."
    "No es solo la idea de ser hipnotizada lo que la emociona."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1076
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_25b4b950:

    # n "Did you really think I'd agree to it? O-or that you could somehow trick me into being your subject and... and mesmerize me against my will?"
    n "¿En verdad creíste que aceptaría? ¿O q-que podrías engañarme para ser tu víctima y... y hechizarme en contra de mi voluntad?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1077
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5506e00c:

    # n front irritated blush "S-seduce my unwitting mind into a stupor so you could reshape it to your own twisted design? Was that it?" with dissolve
    n front irritated blush "¿S-seducir mi mente inconsciente y cautivarla para así remoldearla a tu retorcido diseño? ¿Eso era?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1191
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_1ac8b38f:

    # ncg sleeptalk "It's just... knowing how well your hypnosis has worked on me? It REALLY got my mind racing, Kyou."
    ncg sleeptalk "Es que… ¿saber lo bien que tu hipnosis funcionó en mí? Eso DE VERDAD me voló la mente."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1086
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ee710422:

    # ncg standing sad "All the possibilities I could only imagine before now..." with dissolve
    ncg standing sad "Todas las posibilidades que hasta ahora solo podía imaginar…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1087
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_4eae6638:

    # "Nozomi Akemi. Our class representative and the girl I've dreamed about for years..."
    "Nozomi Akemi. Nuestra representante de clase y la chica con la que he soñado por años…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1088
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a7d154c2:

    # ncg confused "You could... you could make it seem so real!" with dissolve
    ncg confused "Podías… ¡Podías hacerlo parecer tan real!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1089
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b4c082f9:

    # "She was so pure in my mind before. So intimidatingly perfect. So completely out of my league..."
    "Solía ser tan pura en mi mente. Tan intimidantemente perfecta. Tan completamente fuera de mi alcance…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1090
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3883a5f4:

    # "I thought I knew so much about her already..."
    "Creí que ya sabía mucho sobre ella…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1092
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f67dc4a2:

    # ncg surprised "And... a-and oh my gosh, I really AM telling you everything! I-is this too much?" with dissolve
    ncg surprised "Y… y a-ay Dios, ¡SÍ te estoy diciendo todo! ¿Es demasiado?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1093
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_16c567da:

    # "But listening to her now, and watching her push through her obvious embarrassment to bare her soul to me..."
    "Pero al escucharla ahora y verla luchar contra su evidente vergüenza para desnudar su alma ante mí…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1095
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_fa2d44f1:

    # ncg sad "I-I just felt I needed to come clean about it all. Sorry..." with dissolve
    ncg sad "Y-yo solo sentí que tenía que aclararlo todo. Lo siento…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1096
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c41fe07b:

    # ncg drooping sleeptalk "I'm just... I'm making this too weird, aren't I?" with dissolve
    ncg drooping sleeptalk "Solo… lo estoy haciendo que las cosas se pongan muy raras, ¿verdad?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1097
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a576c8b1:

    # "She seems kind of... messed up?"
    "Parece estar un poco… ¿trastornada?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1098
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_2e58154e:

    # ncg sleepy "{size=16}I... I-I barely know you, why am I being like this...{/size}" with dissolve
    ncg sleepy "{size=16}A-apenas te conozco. ¿Por qué estoy actuando así…?{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1099
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9fd0f98e:

    # ks sigh blush "It's... It's okay, Nozomi. But man, this is a lot."
    ks sigh blush "Está… está bien, Nozomi. Pero, caray, esto es mucho."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1100
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_edac2fe8:

    # ncg sleeptalk "Sorry... I've just been thinking about this all day and night." with dissolve
    ncg sleeptalk "Lo siento… He estado pensando en esto día y noche." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1101
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_2c903068:

    # ncg standing confused "I mean, mostly I thought I'm letting myself get carried away; that I should stop all of this." with dissolve
    ncg standing confused "Digo, más que nada pensé que me estaba dejando llevar demasiado; que debería ponerle un alto a esto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1102
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c46cbeb4:

    # ncg stern "Like there's this inner voice screaming at me to stay away from you. Telling me this is all so stupid and dangerous and... and wrong." with dissolve
    ncg stern "Como si hubiera una voz interior gritándome que me aleje de ti. Diciéndome que todo esto es estúpido y peligroso y… que está mal." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1103
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3cb94a69:

    # ncg drooping sleeptalk "But there's this other, much stronger part of me that needs this... s-so badly." with dissolve
    ncg drooping sleeptalk "Pero hay otra parte de mí mucho más fuerte que necesita esto… e-en verdad lo necesita." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1104
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c66e30b6:

    # ncg sleepy "So there it is, Kyou. That's the whole truth about me that I haven't told anyone else. Not even my closest friends." with dissolve
    ncg sleepy "Así que ahí lo tienes, Kyou. He ahí toda la verdad sobre mí la cual no le he contado a nadie más. Ni siquiera a mis más cercanas amigas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1105
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_08babf2c:

    # ncg standing sad "I don't know if that changes anything. If we can keep doing what we were doing, or..." with dissolve
    ncg standing sad "No sé si eso cambia algo. Si podemos seguir haciendo lo que estábamos haciendo o…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1106
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a77db521:

    # "Nozomi trails off as my mind turns."
    "Nozomi se detiene y mi mente no para de dar vueltas."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1213
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b231347b:

    # "So... she really does want to feel like I'm controlling her mind? That's kind of hot and uncomfortable to me all at once."
    "Pues… ¿de verdad quiere sentir que controlo su mente? Eso es un tanto ardiente e incómodo para mí al mismo tiempo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1108
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e70831b9:

    # ncg confused "Look, Kyou, I know I can't pretend we don't know each other in school forever. We... we can work on that." with dissolve
    ncg confused "Mira, Kyou, sé que no puedo fingir que no nos conocemos en la escuela por siempre. Podemos trabajar en eso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1109
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9899ca92:

    # ncg sad "J-just like we can work on giving you more control over what we do together." with dissolve
    ncg sad "A-así como podemos trabajar en darte más control de lo que hacemos juntos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1110
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_149d5cce:

    # ncg neutral "Would that help?" with dissolve
    ncg neutral "¿Eso ayudaría?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1111
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_dc021867:

    # "Man... Even thinking about breaking things off with Nozomi a day ago would've felt like insanity."
    "Cielos… Siquiera pensar en cortar lo que hago con Nozomi hace un día me habría parecido una insensatez."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1112
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5f128134:

    # "Especially when it's like everything's going to plan?"
    "Sobre todo cuando todo está yendo ¿de acuerdo al plan?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1113
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_1e29ff18:

    # "I mean, learning hypnosis really, REALLY was the way to get her attention."
    "Es decir, aprender hipnosis en serio, EN SERIO sí fue la manera de atraer su atención."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1114
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3585c7f5:

    # "But now that it comes to it, is this really, truly what I want to do?"
    "Pero, a estas alturas, ¿es esto real y verdaderamente lo que yo quiero hacer?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1115
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_57be1a0e:

    # "Even after all this it doesn't sound like she's even thinking about dating me."
    "Incluso después de esto no suena a que siquiera esté pensando en salir conmigo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1117
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_bc153b77:

    # "Am I going to go to so much effort to give her what she wants when I'm not sure I'll get anything out of it myself?" with dissolve
    "¿Voy a esforzarme tanto en darle lo que quiere cuando no estoy seguro de si conseguiré algo para mí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1118
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ab29cbe3:

    # "Hell, if she's really as messed-up as this, is she even the kind of person I'd WANT to be with anymore?"
    "Diablos, si de verdad está tan trastornada, ¿siquiera sigue siendo la persona con la que QUERRÍA estar?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1155
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c41bc5d5:

    # ks sigh "Nozomi... I'm sorry."
    ks sigh "Nozomi… Lo lamento."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1156
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_125e3b67:

    # "I have to force the words out of my mouth..."
    "Tengo que sacar esas palabras a la fuerza de mi boca…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1158
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_75eaff20:

    # ks "What you're asking is... th-this is too much." with dissolve
    ks "Lo que estás pidiendo es… e-esto es demasiado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1159
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_1dec1f59:

    # "But I have to face the facts."
    "Pero debo afrontar los hechos."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1161
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_60ffae78:

    # "And so does Nozomi." with dissolve
    "Y Nozomi también." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1162
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_adcccc62:

    # ks frown "I just don't think I can be happy with an arrangement like this."
    ks frown "Simplemente no creo poder ser feliz con un arreglo como este."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1163
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_4c59f66b:

    # ks "S-So..."
    ks "A-así que…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1164
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_d78dfcbc:

    # ncg sleeptalk "You don't need to say anything more, Kyou." with dissolve
    ncg sleeptalk "No tienes que decir nada más, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1165
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_90ab4a5b:

    # ncg "I understand."
    ncg "Entiendo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1176
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_2b101e25:

    # "And just like that, Nozomi shakily gets up to leave."
    "Y así nomás, Nozomi se levanta temblante y se va."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1177
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_7c60132d:

    # n "Thanks, though... For what we did."
    n "Pero, gracias… por lo que hicimos."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1178
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_eabd3b5d:

    # n side sad_side "I'll see you in class." with dissolve
    n side sad_side "Te veré en clase." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1184
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_1d6f23d2:

    # "And just like that, it felt like Nozomi just walked back out of my life."
    "Y así, siento que Nozomi se ha ido caminando de mi vida una vez más."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1187
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9ed39033:

    # "It's been a few weeks since that day."
    "Han pasado algunas semanas desde aquel día."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1193
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c54def67:

    # s "Mmmrrrn...."
    s "Mmmnnnn…."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1194
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_352c3323:

    # h smile_side "Hang in there, buddy. We got culture fest this week, case you forgot." with dissolve
    h smile_side "Aguanta un poco, amiga. Tenemos un festival cultural esta semana, por si se te olvidó." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1195
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_45043994:

    # "A few weeks since Nozomi and I stopped playing with that penlight."
    "Algunas semanas desde que Nozomi y yo dejamos de jugar con esa linterna."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1196
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_88561a53:

    # s rolleyes "As if I needed reminding. I could do without the wasted time." with dissolve
    s rolleyes "Como si necesitara un recordatorio. Preferiría no tener que desperdiciar el tiempo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1200
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e176a9c6:

    # n "I think the change of pace will do you some good, Sayori."
    n "Creo que bajar el ritmo por un rato te vendrá bien, Sayori."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1201
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_48ff1a81:

    # "It's funny though..."
    "Pero es gracioso..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1202
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_06277288:

    # s concerned "Perhaps... Anyway, study club awaits." with dissolve
    s concerned "Quizás… En fin, el club de estudio me espera." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1203
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_47c8f933:

    # "But after that time I spent with Nozomi..."
    "Porque, luego del tiempo que pasé con Nozomi…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1204
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_fe2605e5:

    # s neutral_right "Have a good evening, Kyou." with dissolve
    s neutral_right "Que tengas una buena tarde, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1205
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_0cfdb8d6:

    # "Even if things didn't work out with us..."
