    "Puede que Nozomi haya descubierto algo de sí misma cuando encontró disfrutable el hipnotizarme…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1696
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_bbfb77ac:

    # "Is this something I'm realizing about myself now?"
    "¿Es esto algo que yo estoy descubriendo de mí mismo?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1702
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_6da88d11:

    # "The day passes, and as lunch break begins Nozomi begins to head towards the rooftop with her friends, only to have a thought and say she'll catch up." with dissolve
    "Transcurre el día, y al comenzar la hora del almuerzo, Nozomi se pone en marcha a la azotea con sus amigas, solo para pensarlo dos veces y decir que después las alcanza." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1703
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_b167bd95:

    # "(I need to figure out what exactly Nozo does here, but we find out she left in the trigger from last night and she uses it to mess with Kyou here.)"
    "(Aún necesito pensar en qué es lo que Nozo hace exactamente aquí, pero descubrimos que dejó el ancla de anoche y la usa para jugar con Kyou.)"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1706
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_ed6a8246:

    # "Man, I barely kept it together for the rest of the day."
    "Caray, apenas pude mantener la calma el resto del día."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1708
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_0824c957:

    # n "Stand!" with dissolve
    n "¡De pie!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1709
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_e819aba9:

    # n "Bow!"
    n "¡Reverencia!"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1711
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_a47c7e0c:

    # "Things only got more intense the closer we got to hometime."
    "Las cosas solo se pusieron más intensas entre más cerca estábamos de irnos a casa."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1715
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_6be1059f:

    # h "Seeya later~" with dissolve
    h "’Ta luego." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1716
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_0f31caf6:

    # s smile "See you. And I hope to find you on Sunday giving it your best." with dissolve
    s smile "Hasta luego. Y espero verte el domingo dando lo mejor." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1717
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_d260dd7e:

    # "But it's over now. I can go home."
    "Pero ya se acabó. Puedo irme a casa."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1718
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_e49f587e:

    # h uniform_armup happy "You bet! I'm gettin' pumped just thinking about it~" with dissolve
    h uniform_armup happy "¡Puedes apostarlo! Me siento llena de energía de solo pensarlo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1721
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_a780dc16:

    # n "So you're feeling confident?" with dissolve
    n "Entonces, ¿tienes confianza?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1723
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_e3de1ff9:

    # h uniform annoyed_side "Dunno 'bout confident, but I'm gonna give it everything I've got!" with dissolve
    h uniform annoyed_side "No sé si confianza, ¡pero daré todo lo que tengo!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1724
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_5d142b4a:

    # n laugh "I can't wait to see you in action, Hiroko! It's been too long since I've watched you play." with dissolve
    n laugh "¡No puedo esperar a verte en acción, Hiroko! Hace mucho que no te observo jugar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1725
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_88917bce:

    # h uniform_armup happy blush "Hells, yeah! It means a lot to me that you're gonna be there, you guys~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve
    h uniform_armup happy blush "¡Pero por supuesto que sí! Significa mucho para mí que estén ahí, chicas. {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1726
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_a7b618f1:

    # n smile_side "Aw, of course! Wouldn't miss this for the world~" with dissolve
    n smile_side "Oh, ¡por supuesto! No me lo perdería por nada en el mundo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1728
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_47723b49:

    # "It was all I could do to keep these thoughts I've been having from spilling out in front of everybody."
    "Hizo falta mucho esfuerzo para no escupir estos pensamientos delante de todos."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1730
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_d7e3b982:

    # "And now that we're out, the intensity of these feelings doesn't abate one bit."
    "Y ahora que hemos salido, la intensidad de estos sentimientos no disminuye ni un poco."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1734
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_b2bd4c94:

    # "After all... as I arrive home and crash on the couch, I know I'll soon be able to indulge again."
    "Depués de todo… cuando llego a casa y me desplomo en el sofá, sé que pronto podré volver a sentir satisfacción."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1736
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_f82631a1:

    # "We didn't even need to say anything to each other. We knew she'd be at my door as soon as she dared."
    "Ni siquiera tuvimos que decirnos nada. Sabíamos que ella estaría en mi puerta tan pronto como se atreviera."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1738
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_5f3bad8d:

    # "And I'd be there to greet her."
    "Y que yo estaría ahí para recibirla."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1739
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_8428e4dd:

    # n side smile_side "So..." with dissolve
    n side smile_side "Pues…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1741
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_c892e29d:

    # "As we see the looks on each other's faces, the two of us break into embarrassed laughter." with dissolve
    "Al ver las miradas en los rostros del otro, los dos rompemos en avergonzadas carcajadas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1742
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_6996ce48:

    # "Making it through the day was an ordeal for us both it seems."
    "Llegar al final del día fue una ordalía para ambos, por lo que parece."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1852
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_eaff7879:

    # "As we settle down, we immediately find ourselves drawn to sit in front of each other as we get straight to it."
    "Luego de tranquilizarnos, inmediatamente nos sentamos uno frente al otro, poniéndonos directo manos a la obra."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1748
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_4deb0351:

    # n "S-so, much as I hate to admit it, I actually don't have a lot of time tonight." with dissolve
    n "P-pues, por mucho que odie admitirlo, lo cierto es que no tengo mucho tiempo esta noche." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1749
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_89489277:

    # "... Well, that's one way to bring me straight back down to earth."
    "… Bueno, eso sí me pone los pies de regreso en la tierra."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1750
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_9d7a4d29:

    # ks sigh "Oh..."
    ks sigh "Oh…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1752
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_e2866540:

    # n "Yeah... So I was thinking about how to make the most of things." with dissolve
    n "Sí… Así que estuve pensando en cómo aprovecharlo al máximo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1753
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_e3e130bf:

    # n "A-and... well..."
    n "Y… p-pues…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1754
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_7694d286:

    # "I find myself leaning in towards her a little, anxious to find out what she has in store."
    "Me inclino un poco hacia ella, lleno de ansias por averiguar qué tiene guardado."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1756
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_f74df130:

    # n "There is something I think we could try, and I'm just dying to see if we can make it work." with dissolve
    n "Hay algo que creo que podríamos probar, y muero por ver si podemos hacer que funcione." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1757
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_888058a2:

    # ks smile "So, what is it?"
    ks smile "Y, ¿qué es?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1759
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_40b6ac95:

    # n "It's just... I have to ask first." with dissolve
    n "Es que… debo preguntar primero." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1761
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_1456d387:

    # n "How do you feel about karaoke?" with dissolve
    n "¿Qué opinas del karaoke?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1762
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_53f0d3f8:

    # ks surprised "Huh?!"
    ks surprised "¡¿Eh?!"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1763
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_1ec961c8:

    # "Okay I gotta admit, that came out of left field."
    "Debo admitir que eso me tomó por sorpresa."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1765
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_e5f5fabb:

    # n "It's just... Well, you know about the big tennis tournament this Sunday, don't you?"
    n "Es que… Pues, ya sabes del gran torneo de este domingo, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1766
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_c951f853:

    # ks sigh "Ugh, yeah I do."
    ks sigh "Aj, sí, lo sé."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1767
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_6c8dc974:

    # "I respond out of reflex, and immediately regret it."
    "Respondo por reflejo, arrepintiéndome inmediatamente."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1769
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_3df9a6d9:

    # "But Nozomi simply shrugs it off with a grin." with dissolve
    "Pero Nozomi simplemente se encoje de hombros con una sonrisa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1770
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_7a722a33:

    # n "I know Hiroko isn't your favourite person, but I'm throwing a little karaoke party for everyone after the tournament's over."
    n "Sé que Hiroko no es tu persona favorita, pero haré una pequeña fiesta de karaoke para todos cuando termine el torneo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1772
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_41b11106:

    # n "I'm hoping Hiroko will have something to celebrate by then..." with dissolve
    n "Espero que Hiroko tenga algo que celebrar para entonces…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1773
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_b9669b4a:

    # "Nozomi lets the moment hang before clearing her throat and getting to the point."
    "Nozomi deja que el momento se alargue antes de aclarar su garganta e ir al grano."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1775
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_e94966b8:

    # n "But anyway, I was wondering if you wanted to come along?" with dissolve
    n "Pero, en fin, me preguntaba si te gustaría asistir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1776
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_54e71fad:

    # "She... really wants me to go to this? This triggers a whole bunch of anxieties."
    "¿De… verdad quiere que vaya? Esto despierta un montón de ansiedades."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1777
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_1f9f780b:

    # ks sigh "What's Hiroko gonna say if I'm there? Doesn't she hate me?"
    ks sigh "¿Qué es lo que dirá Hiroko si voy? ¿Qué no me odia?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1779
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_8c63d390:

    # n "Um, well..." with dissolve
    n "Em, pues…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1780
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_89ddc5c1:

    # ks surprised "And... a-and aren't you worried about being seen with me?"
    ks surprised "¿Y… y n-no te preocupa que te vean conmigo?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1782
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_66520315:

    # n "I had thought about that, but Kyou... what's this really about?" with dissolve
    n "Ya había pensado en eso, pero, Kyou… ¿de qué se trata realmente?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1783
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_2f1fb9d2:

    # "I blink at her."
    "Le parpadeo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1785
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_e64564a6:

    # n "Of course I'm a little worried about those things. Of course I thought about them." with dissolve
    n "Claro que me preocupan un poco esas cosas. Por supuesto que pensé en ellas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1786
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_bfb61927:

    # n "But are YOU worried about them, Kyou? Or is it something else?"
    n "¿Pero estás TÚ preocupado por ellas, Kyou? ¿O es algo más?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2045
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_59cd75cd:

    # ks confused "Uh, well..."
    ks confused "Eh, pues…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1788
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_495b9133:

    # "As I struggle to answer, I feel Nozomi's gaze upon me taking in the worry on my face."
    "Mientras me esfuerzo por contestar, siento la mirada de Nozomi sobre mí analizando la preocupación en mi rostro."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1790
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_04456789:

    # "And with a giggle, she claps her hands together as she apparently comes to a conclusion." with dissolve
    "Y con una risa, junta sus manos, aparentemente llegando a una conclusión." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1791
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_420435a2:

    # n "Ahaha, I knew it!"
    n "Jajaja, ¡lo sabía!"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1792
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_23ff52dc:

    # ks frown blush "K-knew what?"
    ks frown blush "¿S-sabías qué?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1794
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_a9e84290:

    # n "It's the singing you're worried about! You've never done karaoke before, have you?" with dissolve
    n "¡Te preocupa lo de cantar! Nunca has hecho karaoke antes, ¿o sí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1795
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_20cc8b34:

    # "I don't answer but my body betrays me, as I feel myself quivering on the couch before her piercing declaration."
    "No respondo, pero mi cuerpo me traiciona. Puedo sentir como tiemblo en el sofá ante su desgarradora declaración."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1797
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_b15ef438:

    # n "Really. Imagine living in this country and being so terrified of singing the hits in front of your friends." with dissolve
    n "En serio. Imagínate vivir en este país y estar tan aterrado de cantar los éxitos frente a tus amigos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1798
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_56be2596:

    # ks frown "Sh-shut up, I'm shy! A-and Hiroko's not my friend and I have a shitty singing voice!"
    ks frown "¡C-cállate, soy tímido! ¡Y-y Hiroko no es mi amiga y mi voz es una mierda para cantar!"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1800
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_af75867a:

    # n "Ahahaha!" with dissolve
    n "¡Jajajaja!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1802
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_eb2179f5:

    # n "It's not about how well you sing! If it was I'd never do it." with dissolve
    n "¡No se trata de qué tan bien cantes! Si así fuera, yo nunca lo haría." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1803
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_de38886e:

    # "... Did she just say she's terrible at singing? Someone like her?"
    "… ¿Acaba de decir que es una terrible cantante? ¿Alguien como ella?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1804
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_49202a8d:

    # "I don't believe that."
    "No le creo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1805
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_540d2b16:

    # n "Kyou, trust me. Everything's going to be fine."
    n "Kyou, créeme. Todo estará bien."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1807
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_c5351a8a:

    # n "You're going to be there, you're going to sing your heart out and everyone's going to have a great time!" with dissolve
    n "¡Irás allá, cantarás con el corazón y todos se la van a pasar genial!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1808
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_6f9564fd:

    # ks sigh "How are you so sure about this?"
    ks sigh "¿Cómo estás tan segura de eso?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1812
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_74e4362d:

    # "And to that, Nozomi simply pops open her schoolbag and pulls out the penlight from inside." with dissolve
    "Y en respuesta, Nozomi simplemente abre su mochila y saca la linterna." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1813
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_551aa5d0:

    # n "Because I'm sure I can calm those nerves of yours with a little hypnosis!"
    n "¡Porque estoy segura de que puedo calmar esos nervios con hipnosis!"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1814
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_e6cb624d:

    # "Okay, seeing that thing again raised my spirits, not gonna lie. But even so..."
    "Muy bien, ver esa cosa otra vez me elevó un poco el espíritu, no mentiré. Pero, aun así…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1816
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_2a388d05:

    # ks surprised "What exactly are you going to do with that?"
    ks surprised "¿Qué harás con eso exactamente?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1818
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_e593217c:

    # n "Wouldn't you rather be surprised by what's in store?" with dissolve
    n "¿No preferirías que sea sorpresa?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1819
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_2dd9d29c:

    # "I could guess that she wants to try making me feel better about this whole thing. But the way she says it..."
    "Supongo que quiere intentar hacerme sentir mejor con todo esto. Pero por como lo dice…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1821
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_d5e40608:

    # n "And besides, I'm running out of time before I have to go, so we really need to get started." with dissolve
    n "Y, además, me estoy quedando sin tiempo antes de tener que irme, así que hay que empezar ya." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1832
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_c754f1ec:

    # "Okay, I kinda trust that she knows what she's doing by now, but the way she's pressuring me into accepting without talking it through first?"
    "Muy bien, creo que, a estas alturas, confío en que sabe lo que hace, pero ¿la forma en la que me está presionando para aceptar sin antes discutirlo?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1833
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_385a4136:

    # "It makes me want to..."
    "Me hace querer…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1839
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_9891f3b3:

    # "... Let's face it, the moment she brought hypnosis into this my heart started racing."
    "… Afrontémoslo, en el momento en que involucró hipnosis en esto, mi corazón se aceleró."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1840
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_8a013614:

    # "I can almost feel my renewed arousal pushing my worries away, because..."
    "Casi puedo sentir mi renovada excitación haciendo a un lado mis preocupaciones, porque…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1841
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_f7cf8021_1:

    # "It feels so good to be hypnotized by Nozomi..."
    "Se siente muy bien ser hipnotizado por Nozomi…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1842
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_9a4f20ca:

    # ks smile "O-okay, yeah. Let's do it."
    ks smile "D-de acuerdo, sí. Hagámoslo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1846
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_24963e71:

    # "Nozomi beams encouragingly at me as she holds the penlight aloft, and as before, my eyes seem drawn to it without me even registering it happening." with dissolve
    "Nozomi me sonríe alentadoramente sosteniendo, la linterna en lo alto; y al igual que antes, mis ojos parecen seguirla sin siquiera darme cuenta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1847
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_5f1c049f:

    # n "Great! So, I'll try to make this quick."
    n "¡Grandioso! Pues, trataré de que sea rápido."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1849
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_e48306eb:

    # "I don't want this to be quick. I want Nozomi to take all the time in the world..."
    "No quiero que sea rápido. Quiero que Nozomi se tome todo el tiempo del mundo…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1850
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_f86599d0:

    # n "That's right, Kyou. It's automatic now, isn't it? How naturally your eyes are drawn up to the light."
    n "Eso es, Kyou. Ya es automático, ¿no? Que tus ojos se enfoquen en la luz de forma tan natural."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1872
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_038fdae2:

    # n "-se and shine, Kyou! Wide awake now."
    n "-ba, arriba, Kyou! Despierta ahora."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1873
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_05f98778:

    # "All of a sudden I'm blinking rapidly as I notice... oh."
    "De la nada estoy parpadeando rápidamente y noto… oh."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1874
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_d8a60a77:

    # "It's over already?"
    "¿Ya se acabó?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1875
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_4d9edb9d:

    # n "How are you feeling?"
    n "¿Cómo te sientes?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1876
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_5e9f7d6d:

    # "As I bring a hand to my head and blink again, I let out a slow sigh."
    "Llevándome una mano a la cabeza y parpadeando una vez más, suelto un lento suspiro."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1877
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_fff25dbb:

    # ks sigh blush "Good..."
    ks sigh blush "Bien…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1878
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_f78358fe:

    # "Yeah. That's what comes out of my mouth. I feel good."
    "Sí. Eso es lo que sale de mi boca. Me siento bien."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1990
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_1cd1aad6:

    # n "I'm glad. Hypnosis is SUPPOSED to feel good! I wanted to make sure of that~" with dissolve
    n "Me alegro. ¡Se SUPONE que la hipnosis se sienta bien! Quise asegurarme de eso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1882
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_f59da915:

    # n "Anyway, I really do have to be going, but we'll meet up again on Sunday morning, alright?" with dissolve
    n "Como sea, de verdad ya me tengo que ir, pero nos veremos el domingo en la mañana, ¿de acuerdo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1883
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_fb06d905:

    # ks surprised "Uh... S-sure."
    ks surprised "Eh… C-claro."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1884
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_56f86281:

    # "As my thoughts swim back into focus, I realize what she's asking me. And what I just agreed to."
    "Cuando mis pensamientos vuelven a enfocarse, me doy cuenta de lo que me está pidiendo. Y a lo que acabo de acceder."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1887
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_e18a2133:

    # n "Great! And don't worry; everything's going to be fine~" with dissolve
    n "¡Grandioso! Y no te preocupes; todo estará bien." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1889
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_bfbe6008:

    # "((Outlining from here on))"
    "((Bosquejo desde aquí))"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1900
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_f703195e:

    # "It's Friday, and I'm walking to school with trepidation once more."
    "Es viernes, y una vez más camino | a la escuela."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1905
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_37287dd0:

    # s "Kyou. I was hoping to catch you."
    s "Kyou. Esperaba encontrarte."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1908
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_61096e4c:

    # "I turn and face the unfamiliar but welcome sight of Sayori approaching me on the way to school."
    "Me doy la vuelta para ver la poco familiar pero bienvenida imagen de Sayori acercándoseme de camino a la escuela."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1909
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_870b060a:

    # ks smile "Sayori! How are you?"
    ks smile "¡Sayori! ¿Cómo estás?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1910
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_16865b50:

    # "She immediately frowns at my question."
    "Frunce el ceño inmediatamente ante mi pregunta."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1911
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c39727d9:

    # s uniform_folded alert_annoyed "I will report that I once again fell into a mindless and deep sleep, regardless of my intent to stay awake." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded alert_annoyed "He de reportar que, una vez más, caí en un profundo sueño libre de todo pensamiento pese a mi intención de mantenerme despierta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2155
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_de7f9ddc:

    # ks confused "Did you expect it to wear off?"
    ks confused "¿Esperabas que se te quitara?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1913
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_cb6760b3:

    # s alert_sleep "I had hoped the effect would wane over time, yes. And it has been a few days now." with dissolve
    s alert_sleep "Esperaba que el efecto se menguara con el tiempo, sí. Y ya pasaron unos cuantos días." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2119
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_93b8a7c5:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "But still, the effect of the sleep trigger on me is as potent as ever. I can only assume the \"[alt_name]\" trigger is the same." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "Y, sin embargo, los efectos de tu anclaje de sueño son tan potentes como siempre. Solo puedo asumir lo mismo de la frase anclada a \"[alt_name]\"." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1915
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_17bb1391:

    # s alert_concerned_right "Perhaps if you had given me more control over my own triggers I would be far less concerned by how entrenched they seem to be in my mind." with dissolve
    s alert_concerned_right "Quizá, si me hubieras dado más control sobre mis propios anclajes, estaría mucho menos desasosegada por cuán atrincherados parecen estar en mi mente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1916
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_a48cb75a:

    # "Still, I can't help but notice that she's looking pretty well-rested AND is here on time. Did she turn in at a decent hour last night on purpose then?"
    "Aun así, no puedo evitar notar que luce muy bien descansada y ADEMÁS llegó a tiempo. ¿Se habrá ido a dormir a una hora decente a propósito?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2160
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_aae67ba4:

    # ks sad "I'm sorry. Do you think I should try to deprogram you?"
    ks sad "Lo lamento. ¿Crees que debería intentar desprogramarte?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2123
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_a980ca29:

    # s uniform "... I may permit you to try. But first, let's see what Nozomi has to say." with dissolve
    s uniform "... Podría permitirte intentarlo. Pero primero veamos qué es lo que Nozomi tiene que decir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2164
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_3a440a48:

    # ks neutral "Right."
    ks neutral "Claro."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1924
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9f68c739:

    # "I walk into class with Sayori as we get the day started."
    "Entro a clase junto a Sayori para empezar el día."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1926
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_87c20d27:

    # "Morning lessons feel tense. I've barely been able to concentrate before, but this is worse."
    "Las lecciones de la mañana se sienten tensas. Antes apenas podía concentrarme, pero esto es peor."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1927
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_431ba9fb:

    # "Obviously I'm excited about the prospect of Nozomi joining our experiments."
    "Obviamente me emociona la expectativa de Nozomi uniéndose a nuestros experimentos."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1928
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_342e80d3:

    # "But would she really volunteer when she finds out I'm involved?"
    "Pero ¿de verdad se anotaría como voluntaria si se entera de que yo estoy involucrado?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1929
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_d4e3ab17:

    # "I can see Sayori talking with her and that nasty tennis girl over lunch. Maybe she's talking to her about it right now?"
    "Puedo ver a Sayori hablando con ella y esa repugnante chica del tenis durante el almuerzo. ¿Tal vez esté hablando al respecto con ella ahora?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1930
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_44068856:

    # "I don't dare get close enough to eavesdrop, so all I can do is eat lunch at my desk and play with my phone as I half-listen to the chatter of my classmates around me."
    "No me atrevo a acercarme lo suficiente para escuchar a escondidas. Solo puedo almorzar en mi escritorio y jugar con mi celular, medio-escuchando las charlas de al lado."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1931
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_85f0c62b:

    # "It's started to bother me, how I'm never part of that chatter."
    "Me empieza a molestar nunca ser parte de esas charlas."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1932
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9b2dbdac:

    # "I've hardly talked to anyone these past few years, until these days I've had with Sayori."
    "Apenas he hablado con nadie en los últimos años, hasta estos días que he compartido con Sayori."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1933
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ac435dcc:

    # "Setting aside our new shared interest, just having someone who'll spend their time with me, smile at me... hell, even argue with me. It's been nice."
    "Dejando de lado nuestro nuevo interés común, el solo tener a alguien que pase tiempo conmigo, me sonría… diablos, hasta que discuta conmigo. Ha sido agradable."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1934
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_286df345:

    # "... Jesus. Am I really this fucking lonely?"
    "… Carajo. ¿De verdad estoy tan solo?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1936
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_735be074:

    # "Finally the moment of truth arrives and I head to the study club at the agreed time."
    "Finalmente llega el momento de la verdad y me dirijo al club de estudio a la hora acordada."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1942
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_3f6304c6:

    # ks surprised "Nozomi?"
    ks surprised "¿Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1943
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_cc5aa275:

    # "She's already here? But I got here as soon as I could and study club only just let out!"
    "¿Ya está aquí? ¡Pero vine tan pronto como pude y el club de estudio apenas acaba de terminar!"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1944
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_712248fa:

    # n frown "I'm sorry, Kyou, but we don't have much time. Sayori already explained everything to me." with dissolve
    n frown "Lo siento, Kyou, pero no tenemos mucho tiempo. Sayori ya me lo explicó todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2150
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_a1e7e5af:

    # n front2 frown "You're just going to hypnotize me and make sure I remember what happened, right? Let's get to it!" with dissolve
    n front2 frown "Simplemente vas a hipnotizarme y asegurarte de que recuerde lo que pasó, ¿correcto? ¡Manos a la obra!" with dissolve

    # game/Kyou 5.rpy:2159
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_b336d78e:

    # "... Sayori and I exchange a look. I'm glad she agreed, but she seems a little... eager?"
    "… Sayori y yo intercambiamos miradas. Me alegra que haya accedido, pero parece un poco… ¿impaciente?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1954
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0408f7ee:

    # ks smile "A-alright then, if you could make yourself comfortable and stare straight ahead at me? Great, and now..."
    ks smile "M-muy bien, pues, por favor, ponte cómoda y mantén la mirada al frente viéndome a mí."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1957
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1f243557:

    # "I take out the penlight and hold it above Nozomi's head as I switch it on."
    "Saco la linterna, la sostengo por encima de la cabeza de Nozomi y la enciendo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1958
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_d69844b6:

    # ks "Keep your head where it is, but look up with your eyes at the light."
    ks "Mantén tu cabeza donde está, pero mira hacia arriba con tus ojos adonde está la luz."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2168
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ad80e50a:

    # "I direct her to replicate as best as I can the first time I hypnotized Sayori." with dissolve
    "La dirijo para replicar lo mejor que puedo la primera vez que hipnoticé a Sayori." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1960
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_71095f68:

    # ks "Very good. Now I want you to focus on the light, taking special note of how it feels as the light passes your eyes."
    ks "Muy bien. Ahora quiero que te concentres en la linterna, prestando especial atención a cómo se siente la luz pasando por tus ojos."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2173
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_b2a6713c:

    # "As I finish my sentence, I steer the light beam over her determined eyes while Sayori looks on."
    "Tras terminar la oración, arrastro el haz por sus determinados ojos mientras Sayori observa."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1967
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_205d3a29:

    # ks "That's right, Nozomi. Just watching the light, taking a deep breath in, that's all you need to do."
    ks "Eso es, Nozomi. Solo observa la luz e inhala profundamente. Eso es todo lo que tienes que hacer."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1969
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_058e6851:

    # ks neutral "And breathe out... relax."
    ks neutral "Y exhala… relájate."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1971
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6922931a:

    # ks "If you find that your eyelids are starting to strain, that your eyes are becoming tired, then that's okay, Nozomi."
    ks "Si tus párpados comienzan a sentirse cansados, si tus ojos se sienten agotados, eso está bien, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1973
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_44c93d2e:

    # ks "Breathe in, and let yourself blink while you look, if you need to."
    ks "Inhala, observa atentamente y parpadea si lo necesitas."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2186
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_d1d56eed:

    # ks "That's it. That's all you need to do, just focus on the light as best as you can. And breathe out."
    ks "Eso es. Eso es todo lo que tienes que hacer. Solo concéntrate en la luz tanto como puedas. Y exhala."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1980
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_750b64e6:

    # ks "Very good, Nozomi. Taking in every feeling, letting it happen if you're becoming sleepy."
    ks "Muy bien, Nozomi. Absorbe cada sentimiento, y si te empieza a dar sueño, solo deja que ocurra."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1982
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1bf7766f:

    # ks "Just watch the light as long as you can. Breathe in."
    ks "Solo observa la luz tanto tiempo como puedas. Inhala."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1984
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_8a17abe9:

    # ks "But if your eyelids are still becoming heavier, and if you need to sleep and drop for me, that's okay. Breathe out."
    ks "Está bien si tus ojos se siguen poniendo pesados, si necesitas dormir y cerrarlos. Exhala."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2197
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_d42e3f42:

    # ks "It's okay, Nozomi. Dropping deep now. Deep asleep."
    ks "Perfectamente bien, Nozomi. Déjate caer muy profundo. Profundamente dormida."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1990
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_bb2cf764:

    # n "..."
    n "…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1991
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4f3c7742:

    # "Sayori leans towards me and whispers."
    "Sayori se inclina hacia mí y susurra."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2038
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_db9ed4c3:

    # s alert_surprised_right "{size=16}Is that truly all it takes?{/size}" with dissolve
    s alert_surprised_right "{size=16}¿En serio solo eso hace falta?{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2205
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e0819cae:

    # "I simply smile at her. I mean, I guess it's not surprising that Nozomi would be just as hypnotizable as Sayori."
    "Simplemente le sonrío. Digo, supongo que no es de sorprenderse que Nozomi sea tan hipnotizable como Sayori."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1995
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_7e79c796:

    # "Not only does she clearly have a smart and creative mind of her own, we also know she's been hypnotized before."
    "No solo está claro que tiene una mente creativa e inteligente, sino que también sabemos que ha sido hipnotizada antes."

    # game/Kyou 5.rpy:2208
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_09b9dcd2:

    # s "{size=16}Well, I suppose there is a cadence to your voice that lends well to getting people to zone out. That is something of a skill you have.{/size}" with dissolve
    s "{size=16}Bueno, supongo que hay cierta cadencia en tu voz que se presta bien a que la gente se pierda en ella. Tienes algo de habilidad.{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1997
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_86f08716:

    # "... I can feel the smile fading from my face as I eyeball her."
    "… Puedo sentir la sonrisa desvanecerse de mi rostro al voltear a verla."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1998
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_dc425904:

    # s alert_smirk_right "{size=16}You should ask her how the light felt.{/size}" with dissolve
    s alert_smirk_right "{size=16} Deberías preguntarle cómo se sintió la luz.{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1999
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_35ceb2cc:

    # "I was getting to that, Sayori. Geez."
    "A eso iba, Sayori. Caray."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2001
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e1e8eab7:

    # ks "Nozomi, as you go deep for me, can you describe how the light in your eyes felt to you, in your own words?" with dissolve
    ks "Nozomi, mientras caes más profundo, ¿puedes describir cómo se sintió tener la luz en tus ojos con tus propias palabras?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2002
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_602bebda:

    # n sleeptalk "Yes..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "Sí…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2004
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6a0bdbf1:

    # "..." with dissolve
    "…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2005
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_83afe388:

    # s uniform alert_neutral_right "..." with dissolve
    s uniform alert_neutral_right "…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2221
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_f82f49fc:

    # ks sigh "... Describe how the light felt, Nozomi."
    ks sigh "… Describe cómo se sintió la luz, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2008
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_49471cac:

    # n sleeptalk "Every time you passed the light across my eyes, it felt like my senses were all lighting up in turn." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "Cada vez que pasabas la luz por mis ojos, sentía que todos mis sentidos se iluminaban." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2009
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c9cf4635:

    # n "It felt so... euphoric. I wanted to stare more, but when you suggested I was sleepy, I realized how sleepy I was getting."
    n "Fue tan… eufórico. Quería seguir mirando, pero cuando dijiste que tenía sueño, me di cuenta de cuánto sueño estaba empezando a sentir."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2010
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9b535b30:

    # n "It just felt so nice to stare and... t-to listen..."
    n "Se sentía tan bien mirar y… e-escuchar…"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2013
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4846121e:

    # s "{size=16}That lines up with what little I remember, and I think this supports my thinking that the light is doing more than you intended.{/size}" with dissolve
    s "{size=16}Eso coincide con lo poco que yo recuerdo, y me parece que respalda mi idea de que la linterna hace más de lo que tenías planeado.{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2014
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c1b2ed49:

    # ks frown "{size=16}You really think so? How would it even do that?{/size}"
    ks frown "{size=16}¿De verdad crees eso? ¿Y cómo haría algo así?{/size}"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2015
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1bde9ded:

    # s alert_annoyed "{size=16}She mentioned feeling euphoric. Perhaps the light is triggering the release of a large amount of dopamines and oxytocins in the brain?{/size}" with dissolve
    s alert_annoyed "{size=16}Mencionó sentir euforia. ¿Quizá la luz está provocando la liberación de grandes cantidades de dopaminas y oxitocinas en el cerebro?{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2016
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_18dea61c:

    # s "{size=16}Such a thing may be stimulating the subject's motivation to remain focused on the pattern the light is emitting.{/size}"
    s "{size=16}Tal cosa podría estar estimulando la motivación del sujeto por mantenerse enfocado en el patrón que emite la linterna.{/size}"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2232
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_7cf690a2:

    # s "{size=16}Such a thing may be stimulating the subject's motivation to remain focused on the pattern the light is emitting.{/size}" with dissolve
    s "{size=16}Ello podría estimular la motivación del sujeto de mantenerse enfocado en el patrón de luz emitido por la linterna.{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2233
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1670116d:

    # s "{size=16}And such a chemical release might also shut down any resistance the subject has to the suggestions you are giving them, practically ensuring that they respond favourably.{/size}"
    s "{size=16}Y dicha liberación química podría además apagar cualquier resistencia que el sujeto pueda tener a las sugestiones que le das, prácticamente asegurando que responda favorablemente.{/size}"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2234
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_35f78ddc:

    # "Sayori pauses for a moment as she appears to ruminate on what she just said, then continues."
    "Sayori hace una pausa, aparentemente ponderando lo que acaba de decir, luego continúa."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2020
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0f9d46b6:

    # s alert_neutral "{size=16}This is pure speculation on my part, and somewhat of a... hollywood explanation? But that is more or less what I consider has happened to me, and is happening to Nozomi right now.{/size}" with dissolve
    s alert_neutral "{size=16}Esta es mera especulación de mi parte, y una explicación un tanto... ¿hollywoodense? Pero es más o menos lo que considero que me ocurrió, y que le está ocurriendo a Nozomi ahora mismo.{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2021
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c677f7fb:

    # s alert_annoyed_right "{size=16}So what I think, Kyou, is this penlight of yours is bypassing a person's ability to reason.{/size}" with dissolve
    s alert_annoyed_right "{size=16}Así que lo que creo, Kyou, es que esa pluma linterna tuya está burlando la habilidad que una persona tiene de razonar.{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2240
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_3375a07c:

    # s "{size=16}People subjected to it will allow themselves to drop into trance and have whole facets of their being altered regardless of their conscious will and desire.{/size}" with dissolve
    s "{size=16}Las personas sometidas a ella caerán en trance y facetas enteras de su ser serán alteradas independientemente de su voluntad y deseos conscientes.{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2023
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_3f2009ad:

    # s alert_surprised_right "{size=16}You could say it is a highly effective brainwashing tool.{/size}" with dissolve
    s alert_surprised_right "{size=16}Se podría decir que es una herramienta de lavado de cerebro altamente efectiva.{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2024
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4fbf4bc0:

    # "I exchange a look with Sayori as I feel my mouth hanging open."
    "Intercambio miradas con Sayori quedándome boquiabierto."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2025
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_7b9e7399:

    # ks surprised "{size=16}A-Are you serious?{/size}"
    ks surprised "{size=16}¿Ha-hablas en serio?{/size}"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2245
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_10c6bc24:

    # s "{size=16}Deadly serious. As I told you, I have been altered against my wishes and you need to take responsibility for that.{/size}"
    s "{size=16}Extremadamente en serio. Como te dije, he sido alterada en contra de mis deseos y tienes que hacerte responsable de eso.{/size}"

