    # "And I know I'll have to be more careful with her now because of it. I need to make sure she doesn't tank her tennis career while I'm doing these kinds of experiments."
    "Y por eso sé que ahora tendré que ser más cuidadoso con ella. Debo asegurarme de que no eche su carrera de tenis por la borda mientras hago esta clase de experimentos."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3379
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_5cdea1e2:

    # "So what to do... I still want to mess with her so she'll think twice about lashing out at me again, but she still needs to be fit for that tournament..." with dissolve
    "Entonces ¿qué hago?... Aún quiero jugar con ella, para que lo pience dos veces antes de volver a agredirme, pero debe estar en forma para ese torneo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3380
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_9c3b4625:

    # "Maybe I can find a way to do both."
    "Tal vez pueda hallar la manera de hacer ambas cosas."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3381
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_f50bb46b:

    # ks smile "Sinking so deep. And now that you're back in this nice, deeply relaxed and suggestible state, I want you to think about your weekend."
    ks smile "Muy, muy profundo. Y ahora que estás devuelta en este sugestionable estado, quiero que pienses en tu fin de semana."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3382
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_5df4743e:

    # ks "You know what you need to do. You need to train tomorrow, and then you need to compete for the tournament."
    ks "Ya sabes lo que debes hacer. Debes entrenar mañana, y luego debes competir en el torneo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3383
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_9b3b8386:

    # ks "And you'll find that while you're doing that over the weekend, while you're training and competing you'll find yourself able to put your entire focus into those things."
    ks "Y notarás que, mientras haces eso el fin de semana, mientras entrenas y compites, podrás poner todo tu enfoque en esas cosas."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3384
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_18e5b1b5:

    # ks "All your stresses and anxieties will vanish to the back of your mind. The tournament will be your one and only concern and you will always perform to the best of your ability."
    ks "Todo tu estrés y ansiedades se quedarán en la parte de atrás de tu mente. Ese torneo será tu única preocupación y siempre sacarás lo mejor de tus habilidades."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3385
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_7dc575c1:

    # ks "You will give nothing but your best for your tennis, Hiroko. Do you understand?"
    ks "No darás menos que lo mejor de ti en el tenis, Hiroko. ¿Comprendes?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3387
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_b8477874:

    # h "Yeah... understand..." with dissolve
    h "Sí... entiendo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3389
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_e3d80fd1:

    # ks smirk "That's good, Hiroko. And there's something else you need to do this weekend." with dissolve
    ks smirk "Qué bien, Hiroko. Y hay una cosa más que necesito que hagas este fin de semana." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3390
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_4149f244:

    # ks "When the tournament is over, and if you find you have won, you will remember that you had my help and that I fulfilled my part of our deal."
    ks "Cuando el torneo haya terminado, y si lo ganaste, recordarás que tuviste mi ayuda y que cumplí mi parte del trato. "

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3391
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_ebf4f17e:

    # ks "It would be only fair of you, after I helped in your victory, that you honour our deal by committing to be my assistant, wouldn't it?"
    ks "Lo más justo de tu parte sería, ya que ayudé en tu victoria, que le hagas honor a nuestro trato comprometiéndote a ser mi asistente, ¿no es cierto?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3393
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_d42be798:

    # h "Y-yeah... only fair of me..." with dissolve
    h "S-sí... justo de mi parte..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3395
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_c3ee71e6:

    # ks "That's right. So if you find you have won your tournament you will drop all your other plans for the day to return to my house just like you did today." with dissolve
    ks "Es correcto. Por lo que, si terminas ganando ese torneo, cancelarás todos tus planes de ese día para volver a mi casa, justo como hiciste hoy." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3397
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_d2c7a79b:

    # ks "I'm going to be performing a little warm-up hypnosis show for a small audience and you will need to do your part as my assistant. Understand?"
    ks "Llevaré a cabo un espectáculo de hipnosis de calentamiento para una pequeña audiencia, y tú tendrás que hacer tu parte como mi asistente. ¿Comprendes?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3399
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_8f3c0130:

    # h "A... a warm-up show...?" with dissolve
    h "¿Un... calentamiento...?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3401
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_67b9dfd0:

    # "I pause a moment. I don't think she's ever responded like that before, where she didn't just acknowledge and agree to what I told her." with dissolve
    "Hago una pausa. Creo que nunca había respondido así, no aceptando simplemente lo que le digo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3402
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_261602e8:

    # "Guess the prospect of being hypnotized before an audience really is that nerve-wracking for her. All the better to break her in gently, then."
    "Supongo que la idea de ser hipnotizada ante una audiencia sí la pone muy nerviosa. Entonces será mejor hacerlo con gentileza."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3403
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_3d0a901a:

    # ks smile "That's right. You need to be comfortable about being hypnotized in front of other people. You need practice, just like you needed to practice your tennis."
    ks smile "Así es. Debes estar cómoda siendo hipnotizada delante de otras personas. Debes practicar, así como necesitas practicar tu tenis."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3404
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_27a3e30b:

    # ks "And you'll be so full of confidence after your big win that this will be the best time to do it, don't you agree?"
    ks "Y estarás tan llena de confianza luego de tu gran victoria, que ese será el mejor momento para hacerlo, ¿no te parece?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3406
