    ks "Y seguirá empeorando si no te cuidas."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3310
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_758307a8:

    # "Mad as she is it seems Hiroko can't, or won't, argue with the logic I placed in her head."
    "Por furiosa que esté, parece que Hiroko no puede, ni va a discutir la lógica que implanté en su cabeza."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3342
