# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1630
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_549890ba:

    # "So maybe she really is as bad as everyone else around here..."
    "Tal vez sí sea tan mala como todos por aquí..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1635
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_718ad7fd:

    # "I lunch at my desk in silence as I try to think things through."
    "Almuerzo en mi escritorio en silencio, intentando reflexionar."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1636
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_bb0e660a:

    # "Nozomi can try all she wants to pretend I don't exist, but the fact is, she has something that belongs to me."
    "Nozomi puede intentar fingir que no existo todo lo que quiera, pero el hecho es que ella tiene algo que me pertenece."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1637
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_dad7dd49:

    # "And she can't avoid me forever, so..."
    "Y no puede evitarme por siempre, así que..."

