translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_68529fda:

    # "But... man, is she really going to tell me where she lives? I thought she wanted to keep all this hypnosis stuff to my place?"
    "Pero... cielos, ¿en serio me va a decir dónde vive? Creí que quería mantener todo esto de la hipnosis en mi casa."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1673
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4d531eda:

    # "This is... unexpected."
    "Eso es... inesperado."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1676
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fb538e73:

    # "The rest of the day passed uncomfortably."
    "El resto del día pasó muy incómodamente."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1677
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_dec5a510:

    # "Nozomi went back to ignoring me when she returned from lunch."
