translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_8352b4b0:

    # "Huh. This is a pretty well-to-do area. Not too different from where I live, actually."
    "Vaya. Esta es un área bastante bien acomodada. No muy diferente de donde yo vivo, de hecho."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1687
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b88fe1bb:

    # "But Nozomi never seemed very rich to me. I dunno, maybe she just didn't want to flaunt it."
    "Pero Nozomi nunca me dio la impresión de ser muy rica. No sé, tal vez no quería alardear."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1688
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7c37e918:

    # "... Or maybe this isn't actually her address."
    "... O tal vez esta no es su verdadera dirección."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1689
