    # "It's Friday, and I face the day ahead with another long sigh."
    "Es viernes, y yo encaro el día con otro largo suspiro."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2858
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_27f9cc03:

    # "I ended up spending most of my night reading more about hypnosis and the concept of using it for effecting personality changes."
    "Terminé pasando casi toda la noche leyendo más sobre hipnosis y el concepto de usarla para efectuar cambios en la personalidad."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2859
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_412490ff:

    # "But for all my reading into it, I'm still no closer to understanding why Sayori freaked out the way she did."
    "Pero aun con todo lo que leí, no estoy ni un paso más cerca de entender por qué Sayori se asustó así."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2861
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_70241b6f:

    # "Everything I've seen suggests that Sayori wouldn't have accepted my suggestions, wouldn't have embraced her \"[alt_name]\" persona so fully, unless she seriously wanted to."
    "Todo lo que vi sugiere que Sayori no habría aceptado mis sugestiones ni adoptado tan plenamente su personaje de \"[alt_name]\", salvo que en serio lo haya querido."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2862
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0e33c136:

    # "If she accepted the idea of becoming a separate person the way I told her, then she must have agreed with me on some level."
    "Y si aceptó la idea de convertirse en una persona diferente como le dije, debió haber estado de acuerdo en cierta medida."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2863
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6cfaa0dd:

    # "She really has to feel she needed to let her hair down. Just like she agreed that she needed to get more sleep."
    "Realmente debe sentir que necesita relajarse. Así como estuvo de acuerdo en que necesitaba dormir."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2864
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_84854a66:

    # "It probably just surprised her that deep down she truly was looking for an excuse to let go, and that I would be the one to give it to her."
    "Probablemente solo la sorprendió que en el fondo sí estuviera buscando una excusa para dejarse llevar, y que fuera yo quien se la diera."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2868
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_af4e6ce1:

    # "Or she actually has feelings for me that she didn't want to admit? Maybe that's why she freaked out so much."
    "¿O de verdad tiene sentimientos por mí que no quiere admitir?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2869
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a0c13e3d:

    # "Well, hopefully now she's had a day to think about it Sayori will realize that about herself."
    "Bueno, con suerte ahora que ha tenido un día para pensar Sayori se dará cuenta por sí misma."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2870
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_76995d21:

    # "Sayori, she's... she's smart. And so, so studious. She must have been thinking about this stuff as much as I have."
    "Sayori es... es inteligente. Y muy, muy estudiosa. Debió haber estado pensando en esto tanto como yo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2871
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_3ad7fe1a:

    # "She'll know I'm not trying to do anything bad to her, and she'll want to talk to me again. She'll want to understand the reactions she's had to my hypnosis."
