# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2952
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_34ccbd21:

    # "I'm about to say \"Regret what?\" before I notice her placing a folded-up piece of note paper down on my desk."
    "Estoy por decir \"¿Arrepentirte de qué?\", pero entonces la noto colocando un trozo de papel doblado en mi escritorio."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2964
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_1d409cdd:

    # n front2 sigh "Alright, then. We'll meet tomorrow at 12 o'clock, and I'll expect you to be on your best behaviour." with dissolve
    n front2 sigh "Muy bien. Nos veremos mañana a las 12 en punto, y espero un comportamiento impecable." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2980
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_11052482:

    # "The rest of my day was uneventful, if a little tense."
    "El resto del día transcurre sin eventos, solo con algo de tensión."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2982
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_c717b354:

    # "I'm still on shaky ground with Sayori, and Nozomi too. So I didn't so much as look their way for the rest of the day if that's how they want to play it."
    "Sigo sobre hielo delgado con Sayori, y también con Nozomi. No me atreví ni a mirar en su dirección por el resto del día si así es como quieren que sea."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2983
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_87fc40f2:

    # "But tomorrow I'll be able to make my case and everyone will start to see sense at last."
    "Pero mañana podré defenderme y hacer que por fin entren en razón."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2992
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_95bc82c4:

    # "Hypnosis isn't magic, and neither is this penlight I've constructed. Everyone's got to know that, right?"
    "La hipnosis no es magia, ni tampoco lo es esta linterna que construí. Todos deben saberlo, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2993
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_f781f2c8:

    # "Even if it had a bigger effect on Sayori than I could've imagined. Is the patterning I imprinted on it really that captivating for her?"
    "Incluso si tuvo un mayor efecto en Sayori del que pude imaginar. ¿Es el patrón que le imprimí realmente tan cautivador para ella?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2994
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6d6b0757:

    # "Kinda makes me wonder if it would somehow have the same effect on someone else..."
    "Me hace preguntarme si tendría el mismo efecto en alguien más..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2996
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d1893950:

    # "Ugh, no, I can't think like that. That's the kind of thinking that got me in trouble with Sayori in the first place."
    "Aj, no, no puedo pensar así. Esa es la clase de ideas que me metió en problemas con Sayori en primer lugar."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2997
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6e21ab5c:

    # "I have to set things straight with her first. I need to show her she's got no reason to be scared of me, or of hypnosis."
    "Tengo que arreglar las cosas con ella primero. Debo mostrarle que no tiene razón para temerme, o a la hipnosis."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3000
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_f0427725:

    # "Sayori's a logical person when it comes down to it. So if I can just sit down with her and explain everything rationally, I'm sure she'll see sense..."
    "Sayori es una persona lógica al final del día. Así que, si me siento a explicarle todo racionalmente, estoy seguro de que entenderá..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3002
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2993e264:

    # "... Won't she?"
    "... ¿Verdad?"
# TODO: Translation updated at 2022-12-21 14:04

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3210
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_3beb03a2:

    # h nervous_side "Everything okay? I'm still worried about you after... well, y'know." with dissolve
    h nervous_side "¿Todo en orden? Sigo preocupada por ti después de... bueno, ya sabes." with dissolve


# TODO: Translation updated at 2023-03-29 09:27

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2584
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_b878abee:

    # "I smile as I pull the penlight back out of my pocket. Its reappearance is enough to make Nozomi let out a little squeal of delight."
    "Con una sonrisa saco la linterna de mi bolsillo. Su reaparición hace que Nozomi dé un chillido de alegría."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2585
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_097b9b30:

    # ks smile "Alright, I guess there's something we can do that might help."
    ks smile "Muy bien, supongo que sí hay algo que podemos hacer que podría ser de ayuda."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2586
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_0c52b58f:

    # n chuckle "It'll definitely help~ A simple in and out of trance just isn't going to cut it." with dissolve
    n chuckle "Definitivamente. Algo tan simple como entrar y salir de un trance no será ni de cerca suficiente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2588
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_72d4cc50:

    # "Man, the way her face lit up as soon as I agreed to hypnotize her again... Is this really because she wants to help Sayori?"
    "Cielos, la forma en que se iluminó su rostro en cuanto acepté hipnotizarla otra vez... ¿En serio es porque quiere ayudar a Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2589
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_73c349f5:

    # n smile "For Sayori's sake, I think we owe it to her to be a little more thorough." with dissolve
    n smile "Por Sayori, creo que debemos ser un poco más exhaustivos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2590
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_364f2bc7:

    # "Well, whatever. I'm just happy if I can make her smile at me like this."
    "Bueno, ¿qué importa? Yo estoy feliz si puedo hacerla sonreír así."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2377
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_380b4bc8:

    # n side smile "So I'm going to make myself comfortable in the chair again and we'll start whenever you're ready." with dissolve
    n side smile "Me pondré cómoda en la silla y empezamos cuando estés listo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2592
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_3a39bf24:

    # "This is what I've wanted ever since I started learning about hypnosis. It's why I worked on this penlight in the first place."
    "Esto es lo que he querido desde el momento en que empecé a aprender hipnosis. Es la razón por la que trabajé en esta linterna en primer lugar."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2596
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_1246eb18:

    # "So, yeah... Yeah, let's do this."
    "Así que, sí... Sí, hagámoslo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2597
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_cf55a931:

    # ks smile "Okay so I'll try hypnotizing you just like before, only this time I'll give you a simple post-hypnotic suggestion to follow and we'll see how that effects you."
    ks smile "Muy bien, pues intentaré hipnotizarte igual que antes, solo que esta vez te daré una sugestión posthipnótica simple y veremos cómo te afecta."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2599
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_4cbb664d:

    # n "Sounds good to me!" with dissolve
    n "¡Suena bien para mí!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2601
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_9b3aa216:

    # n "What sort of suggestion, though?" with dissolve
    n "Pero ¿qué clase de sugestión?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2602
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_d6862c33:

    # "Well that's a good question. It's not like I've planned this at all."
    "Buena pregunta. No tengo ningún plan."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2603
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_01e3ebca:

    # ks neutral "Hmm... well..."
    ks neutral "Mmm... pues..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2604
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_e8efe033:

    # "I need to think fast while we're still in the moment."
    "Debo pensar rápido mientras seguimos en el momento."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2605
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_23449ab9:

    # ks confused "Maybe... we could try to alter your senses for a while?"
    ks confused "¿Tal vez... podamos intentar alterar tus sentidos por un rato?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2609
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_22134048:

    # "Nozomi tilts her head slightly as she looks thoughtful." with dissolve
    "Nozomi inclina ligeramente la cabeza con una mirada pensativa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2610
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_06eebfe8:

    # n "Oh? Like getting me to hallucinate something or...?"
    n "¿Oh? ¿Como hacerme alucinar algo o...?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2611
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_35f27fff:

    # "I simply smile at her as I follow through with the hasty idea taking form in my head."
    "Simplemente le sonrío mientras continúo formando la idea apresurada en mi cabeza."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2612
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_269b2902:

    # ks smile "Something like that. Want to see if we can do it?"
    ks smile "Algo así. ¿Quieres ver si podemos hacerlo?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2614
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_18ff8862:

    # "She smiles back as she nods, seemingly eager for the challenge." with dissolve
    "Me devuelve la sonrisa y asiente, aparentemente entusiasmada por el desafío." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2615
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_9da9df9e:

    # n "Of course! And I'm sure our findings will be a big help for Sayori no matter what."
    n "¡Por supuesto! Y estoy segura de que nuestros hallazgos serán de gran ayuda para Sayori sin importar qué."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2616
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_c88a7514:

    # "Great. This is great. So I'll do this, but not for Sayori."
    "Bien. Excelente. Entonces haremos esto, pero no por Sayori."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2617
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_ec32a1b5:

    # ks "Perfect. So let's have your attention here now, back with the light."
    ks "Perfecto. Ahora tu atención aquí, de regreso a la luz."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2619
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_2cea49fc:

    # "This is all for you, Nozomi." with dissolve
    "Esto es por ti, Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2622
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_1c39df96:

    # ks "That's right, just sit back, relax, and watch the light with your eyes."
    ks "Eso es, acomódate, relájate y observa la luz con tus ojos."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2623
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_86665c82:

    # "I'll show you just how fun hypnosis can be."
    "Te mostraré lo divertida que la hipnosis puede ser."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2626
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_bfd34e57:

    # ks neutral "Taking a deep breath now as the light hits you. Feel that breath in your lungs..."
    ks neutral "Respira profundo mientras recibes la luz. Siente ese aire en tus pulmones..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2627
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_4f19aee5:

    # "I'll give you a safe and unforgettable experience."
    "Te daré una experiencia segura e inolvidable."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2630
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_b237908c:

    # ks "... and let it all out now, slowly, allowing a wave of deep relaxation to wash over you."
    ks "... y ahora déjalo salir, lentamente, sintiendo una ola de profunda relajación expandiéndose por tu cuerpo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2631
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_ef816c6d:

    # "Sayori might get mad with me when she finds out but come on, I've learned so much after my time with her."
    "Puede que Sayori se moleste conmigo cuando se entere, pero vamos, he aprendido mucho después de mi tiempo con ella."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2634
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_b97180bb:

    # ks "You can allow yourself to relax, just as you can allow everything else to fade far into the background."
    ks "Puedes relajarte, dejando que todo en el fondo se desvanezca."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2635
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_cd3e7e69:

    # "I won't make the same mistake this time."
    "No cometeré el mismo error esta vez."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2638
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_4c4f3c7b:

    # ks "Leaving just the sight of the light and the patterns it leaves in your eyes..."
    ks "Hasta que solo quede la luz y los patrones que deja ante tus ojos."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2639
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_6c841223:

    # "I... I KNOW what I'm doing here."
    "Yo... yo SÉ lo que estoy haciendo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2642
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_eabf8011:

    # ks "Leaving only the sound of my voice... as you take another breath now, Nozomi."
    ks "Que solo quede el sonido de mi voz... respirando una vez más, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2647
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_cd4fabb9:

    # ks "Breathing in... eyes heavy, thoughts fading..."
    ks "Inhala... y tus ojos pesan, tus pensamientos se desvanecen..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2650
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_77f499a5:

    # ks "Breathing out... eyes closing as you drop into a deep..."
    ks "Exhala... y tus ojos se cierran, cayendo muy profundo y..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2655
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_72378276:

    # ks "Sleep."
    ks "Duerme."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2657
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_33f795ca:

    # n "..." with dissolve
    n "..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2659
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_7055d61e:

    # "Nozomi's shoulders sag and her head rolls forward as she seems to drop into a deep trance just like before."
    "Los hombros de Nozomi se aflojan y su cabeza cae hacia adelante, cayendo en un profundo trance igual que antes."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2662
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_cff8910d:

    # "It seems she really is every bit as good as Sayori was at being hypnotized."
    "Parece que es igual de buena que Sayori en ser hipnotizada."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2663
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_b2f789f4:

    # ks "That's right, Nozomi. Dropping deep now into a comforting state of hypnotic trance."
    ks "Eso es, Nozomi. Cae muy profundo en un acogedor estado de trance hipnótico."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2664
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_2f993bf2:

    # "Because she really wanted to be hypnotized? Or is this really all down to the penlight like Sayori said?"
    "¿Es porque en serio quería ser hipnotizada? ¿O es todo gracias a la linterna como Sayori dijo?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2665
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_5c5d6c59:

    # ks "And while you're in this nice comfortable state, I'd like you to think about... lemons."
    ks "Y mientras estás en este acogedor y agradable estado, quiero que pienses en... limones."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2666
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_b8e98c25:

    # "Well, let's not worry about that for now."
    "Bueno, no nos preocupemos por eso de momento."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2668
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_725d1a2a:

    # n "... Lemons?" with dissolve
    n "... ¿Limones?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2669
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_5d012546:

    # "Right now I just want to focus on having a little fun with the girl I admire so much..."
    "Ahora mismo solo quiero concentrarme en divertirme con la chica que tanto admiro..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2671
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_ce8ffa68:

    # ks "That's right. I'd like you to imagine what it's like to bite into a whole lemon. To tear your teeth into its yellow flesh and feel the bitter juice squirt into your mouth." with dissolve
    ks "Así es. Quiero que imagines morder un limón entero. Encajar tus dientes en su cáscara amarilla y sentir el jugo amargo chorreando en tu boca." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2672
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_d70734e0:

    # n "M... mmmmn..."
    n "M... mmmmn..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2673
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_1ab5de5b:

    # "I grin as Nozomi's cute features start to contort from the mental image I'm making for her."
    "Sonrío al ver las lindas facciones de Nozomi contorsionarse por la imagen mental que le estoy dando."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2674
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_6386e7f8:

    # ks smile "Can you taste the lemon, Nozomi?"
    ks smile "¿Puedes saborear el limón, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2676
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_b641f75e:

    # n "Y...y-yeah..." with dissolve
    n "S... s-sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2677
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_c12247c6:

    # ks "Can you feel the bitter citrus taste in your mouth as it seems to set your teeth on edge?"
    ks "¿Puedes sentir el amargo sabor cítrico en tu boca que estremece hasta tus dientes?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2678
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_5c72970b:

    # n "Ugh... yes..."
    n "Aj... sí..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2679
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_3e2a86e0:

    # ks "Feel the overpowering scent of lemon as it assaults your taste buds and works its way deep into your nostrils?"
    ks "Siente el abrumador aroma del limón que invade tus papilas gustativas y llega a lo más profundo de tus fosas nasales."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2680
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_92e8a35d:

    # "Now I have to stifle a laugh as the poor girl nearly gags at the sensation."
    "Ahora no puedo evitar reír al ver la cara de nausea que la pobre chica pone ante la sensación."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2681
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_ab167e62:

    # n "Urrrrrghhh... y-yesh..."
    n "Aaaayyyyyy... s-sí..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2682
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_b18c5cc5:

    # "Maybe I went a little overboard, but I kinda need it to be for what I'm about to suggest to her next."
    "Tal vez me pasé un poco, pero es necesario para la sugestión que le daré después."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2677
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_675ad789:

    # ks "That's good. Now, when you awaken from this trance you will find that anything you eat will feel exactly the same as it does to bite into a whole lemon, just as you are now." with dissolve
    ks "Muy bien. Ahora, cuando despiertes de este trance, notarás que todo lo que comas se sentirá exactamente igual que morder un limón entero, como estás haciendo ahora." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2685
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_2d8412d0:

    # ks "The way it tastes, the way it smells, the way it feels in your mouth..."
    ks "Su sabor, su olor, la sensación en tu boca..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2686
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_ceb520ff:

    # ks "No matter what it looks like, anything you eat will give you the exact same experience as if you were eating this lemon. Understand?"
    ks "Sin importar cómo luzca, cualquier cosa que comas te dará la misma sensación que si estuvieras comiendo este limón. ¿Comprendes?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2688
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_56d76425:

    # n "Yes... I understand..." with dissolve
    n "Sí... comprendo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2690
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_0ebc4442:

    # ks "Wonderful. This state of mind will continue only until you hear me snap my fingers." with dissolve
    ks "Maravilloso. Este estado mental continuará únicamente hasta que me escuches chasquear mis dedos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2691
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_e4eac79f:

    # ks "The moment you hear me snap my fingers, all your senses of taste, smell and feeling will return to their natural states."
    ks "En cuando me escuches chasquear los dedos, todos tus sentidos de gusto, olfato y tacto regresaran a sus estados naturales."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2692
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_90598630:

    # ks "You will be completely back to normal with no lasting effects from this hypnotic experience. Is that clear, Nozomi?"
