translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_a165dd97:

    # "And without her, it seems Nozomi feels more free to express how she really feels about all this."
    "Y sin ella, parece que Nozomi se siente más libre de expresar cómo realmente todo esto la hace sentir."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2717
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_acc081cf:

    # n "Yeah! The first time you did this I was a bit tense, but the moment that light hit my eyes it was just so easy to let go." with dissolve
    n "¡Sí! La primera vez que lo hiciste estaba un poco tensa, pero tan pronto la luz tocó mis ojos, se sintió muy fácil dejarme llevar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2718
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_63089508:

    # "Nozomi really does seem to be into this hypnosis stuff. Just like I knew she'd be."
    "Realmente parece que a Nozomi le gusta esto de la hipnosis. Justo como pensé."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2720
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_104ef9da:

    # n "And this second time? I... w-well, I can barely remember a thing about it. I saw the light and then it's like I was suddenly spirited off to a far-away place." with dissolve
    n "¿Y en esta segunda vez? P-... p-pues, no recuerdo casi nada. Vi la luz y es como si hubiera viajado repentinamente a un lugar lejano." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2721
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_3ca4e4e3:

    # "The way her eyes just seem to light up all on their own as she goes on about her experience..."
    "La forma en que sus ojos parecen iluminarse por sí mismos mientras relata su experiencia..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2722
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_24f3d9cb:

    # n "Just, like... wow. I've been hypnotized a few times before in my life but this was something else. It's incredible!"
    n "Es, o sea... guau. He sido hipnotizada un par de veces antes en mi vida, pero esto no se compara. ¡Es increíble!"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2724
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_032d9096:

    # n "Maybe even... Maybe this is the first time I've actually, truly been hypnotized." with dissolve
    n "Tal vez incluso... Tal vez sea la primera vez que he sido real y verdaderamente hipnotizada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2725
