    # "Nozomi purses her lips in thought while her eyes wander, before she notices the clock up on the study club wall."
    "Nozomi frunce pensativamente los labios mientras sus ojos divagan, para luego notar el reloj en la pared del club de estudio."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2836
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_b10342b6:

    # n smile "Anyway, I should get going. Don't want to be late for dinner." with dissolve
    n smile "En fin, ya me tengo que ir. No quiero llegar tarde a cenar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2837
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_4d5dc7bd:

    # ks smile "Oh... s-sure, I'll clean up in here and close up."
    ks smile "Oh... c-claro, yo limpiaré aquí y cerraré."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2838
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_9549164a:

    # n happy "Okay. Have a good weekend, Kyou~" with dissolve
    n happy "De acuerdo. Ten un buen fin de semana, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2840
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Hypno_Nozomi_8dcbb567:

    # "As I go to grab my things, I'm still buzzing with how well that went." with dissolve
