    "{size=30}CONTINUARÁ...{/size}"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4279
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_41e9f09a:

    # "And back to anger again, as I awkwardly watch her pull off her footwear before she follows me into the house proper."
    "Y enojo otra vez. Luego se quita torpemente su calzado antes de seguirme a la sala."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4312
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_9f1b7cf1:

    # h "Like... s-sure, maybe there's a little voice inside me saying I owe you; like I deserved to let you prank me like that." with dissolve
    h "O sea... s-sí, tal vez haya una vocecita dentro de mí diciendo que te debo una; como si me mereciera dejarte hacerme esa jugarreta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4705
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_5fee3a54:

    # ks "And don't you think you're overreacting? I know this has to be weird for you, but I'm asking you again: Have I really done anything to hurt you?"
    ks "¿Y no crees que estás exagerando? Sé que debe ser raro para ti, pero en serio, preguntaré otra vez: ¿He hecho alguna vez algo para lastimarte?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4374
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_a14e20cf:

    # ks neutral "Oh... That's right."
    ks neutral "Oh... Es cierto."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4380
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_98b128c7:

    # ks smile "I... kinda suggested you would be when I hypnotized you yesterday, didn't I?" with dissolve
    ks smile "Te... dije que eso sentirías cuando te hipnoticé ayer, ¿no es cierto?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4386
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_9b81f72a:

    # "It makes me feel like I can do anything with that fascinating little mind of hers. Anything I want."
    "Me hace sentir que puedo hacer cualquier cosa con esa fascinante mentecita suya. Lo que sea que quiera."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4387
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_09e850d9:

    # "But after what she was saying I'm not so sure I should anymore."
    "Pero después de lo que dijo, ya no estoy tan seguro de si debería."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4388
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_d928bd5c:

    # "Hiroko admitted I've been a help to her, even admitted she owes me for all the shit she's put me through."
    "Hiroko admitió que la he ayudado, incluso admitió que me debe una por toda la mierda por la que me ha hecho pasar."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4389
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_9fb3521d:

    # "She sounded almost... reasonable?"
    "Sonó casi... ¿razonable?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4390
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_66ee74af:

    # "So maybe it's time I stopped playing games and heard her out some more."
    "Entonces, tal vez sea hora de dejar de jugar y escucharla un poco más."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4418
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_9ddc378a:

    # ks neutral "I want you to listen closely now, Hiroko. It's very important that you understand everything that I'm saying to you now."
    ks neutral "Ahora quiero que me escuches atentamente, Hiroko. Es muy importante que entiendas todo lo que te voy a decir."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4419
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_b9d7e02f:

    # "As much as I hate to admit, while tricking her has been fun I can't shake off the guilt I've started to feel about this."
    "Por mucho que odie admitirlo, si bien engañarla ha sido divertido, no puedo ignorar la culpa que he estado empezando a sentir."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4420
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_76a19bb7:

    # ks "You don't need to yawn in class when you feel your phone vibrate, you don't need to keep it in your pocket and you don't need to feel hypnotized in my presence."
    ks "No tienes que bostezar en clase cuando sientas tu teléfono vibrar, no tienes que mantenerlo en tu bolsillo y no tienes que sentirte hipnotizada en mi presencia."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4421
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_50dc97d0:

    # "Hiroko's a pain in my ass, but she's got a point. I've been too hung up about getting revenge for what she did to me."
    "Hiroko es un dolor de huevos, pero tiene razón. Me concentré demasiado en conseguir venganza por lo que me hizo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4749
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_25ac2963:

    # ks "You don't need to come see me at my house if you don't want to. In fact, there is no need for you to follow any suggestion I have made, or will make in the future."
    ks "No necesitas venir a verme a mi casa si no quieres. De hecho, no tienes que seguir ninguna sugestión que haya hecho, o que haga en el futuro."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4423
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_ae9408bf:

    # "And besides, after what went down in school today I guess I can call it even."
    "Y además, después de lo que pasó en la escuela hoy, supongo que estamos a mano."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4424
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_5b343ebd:

    # ks "Even if you're hypnotized, it doesn't mean you're compelled to act as I tell you. Any suggestions I make to you under hypnosis are just that: Suggestions."
    ks "Incluso si estás hipnotizada, no significa que estés obligada a actuar como te diga. Cualquier sugestión que te dé bajo hipnosis no es más que una sugerencia."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4425
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_47290da2:

    # ks "How you respond to my suggestions are always, without exception, entirely up to you."
    ks "Como respondas a mis sugestiones siempre y sin excepción depende enteramente de ti."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4426
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_0cddf292:

    # "So that's enough. I'll set her straight about what it means to be hypnotized, and when she comes to she'll listen to me and we can both talk about this like reasonable adults."
    "Así que ya es suficiente. Le dejaré en claro lo que significa ser hipnotizada, y cuando despierte me escuchará y ambos hablaremos como adultos responsables."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4427
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_7fcbfd65:

    # ks "Do you understand what I'm telling you, Hiroko?"
    ks "¿Comprendes lo que te estoy diciendo, Hiroko?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4428
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_0566a207:

    # "... I mean, she IS going to be reasonable now, right?"
    "... Porque SÍ va a ser razonable, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4446
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_fc29c0c6:

    # h "Yeah... I understand." with dissolve
    h "Sí... entiendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4448
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_9b20c06b:

    # ks "Good. So keeping that in mind, I'd like you to remember everything about this trance and wake up on a count of three." with dissolve
    ks "Bien. Y con eso en mente, quiero que recuerdes todo lo que ocurrió en este trance cuando despiertes a la cuenta de tres." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4449
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_52cf57f4:

    # ks "Then we can talk about this some more, okay?"
    ks "Entonces podremos hablar más sobre esto, ¿está bien?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4451
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_26f74f57:

    # h "Okay..." with dissolve
    h "Bien..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4453
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_c0c3424c:

