    h "Eeeemm..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4460
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_0f5692a7:

    # "I give her a moment for those sleepy green eyes to blink back into life, then I start to address her quietly."
    "Le doy un momento para que esos soñolientos ojos verdes regresen a la vida, luego comienzo a hablarle suavemente."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4462
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_8b54abd9:

    # ks "Alright, so you got hypnotized again while we were talking just now, but it's okay. You should be feeling more in control of yourself now."
    ks "Muy bien, pues caíste hipnotizada otra vez mientras hablábamos, pero descuida, ya deberías sentirte en control de ti misma."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4464
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_39bcd79e:

    # ks "No more pranks, no more trying to do things with you that you're not happy with; we're just going to talk like you wanted. That alright with you?" with dissolve
    ks "No más bromas, no más intentar hacer cosas contigo que con las que no estés feliz; simplemente vamos a hablar como querías. ¿Te parece bien?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4466
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_a597c8f5:

    # h "Uhh... y-yeah, 'course it's alright." with dissolve
    h "Eeeh... s-sí, claro que sí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4467
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_a8a29729:

    # "So she says, but I have to wonder with that dark expression she's wearing on her face."
    "Eso dice, pero esa oscura expresión en su rostro me genera algo de duda."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4468
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_2cdb10f5:

    # ks confused "What's the matter now? You don't believe me?"
    ks confused "¿Qué pasa? ¿No me crees?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4470
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_a1de43fc:

    # h "No, I... fuck, I dunno it's just... like..." with dissolve
    h "No, es que... carajo, no sé, es solo que... o sea..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4472
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_e9d94773:

    # h "Don'tcha think it's weird that you gotta tell me not to do this shit? I can't do it by myself?" with dissolve
    h "¿No crees que es raro que tengas que decirme que no haga esta mierda? ¿No puedo hacerlo sola?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4473
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_fd804f20:

    # ks frown "Uh... well, I mean..."
    ks frown "Eh... bueno, este..."

