# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2791
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_1429e458:

    # ks "Tomorrow at my place then? I'll be home alone all day so no one will bother us."
    ks "¿Mañana en mi casa, entonces? Tengo el lugar para mí solo todo el día, así que no habrá nadie que nos moleste."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2886
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_488a6834:

    # "But for all my reading into it, I still can't understand how Sayori was affected the way she seemed to be."
    "Pero por más que leí, aún no puedo entender cómo es que Sayori resultó afectada de esa forma."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2887
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_cd7c7f59:

    # "I just don't get how she fell so deep into the suggestion that she forgot who or where she was while she embraced the \"[alt_name]\" persona with such gusto."
    "No entiendo cómo es que cayó tan profundo en la sugestión que olvidó quién era y dónde estaba mientras adoptaba la personalidad de \"[alt_name]\" con tanto gusto."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2888
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9137efb2:

    # "Everything I've read suggested that Sayori wouldn't have accepted such a state unless she seriously wanted to."
    "Todo lo que leí sugiere que Sayori no habría aceptado tal estado a no ser que quisiera."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2889
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2a2037fb:

    # "If she accepted the idea of becoming a separate person the way I told her, then she must have agreed with it on some level."
    "Si aceptó la idea de convertirse en una persona diferente como le dije, ¿debió estar de acuerdo en cierta medida?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2890
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_42ce5518:

    # "But to embrace it so much that she actually seemed to be completely unaware of her time as [alt_name]? Was it out of shock in the moment, or..."
    "Pero ¿sumergirse tanto que parecía estar completamente inconsciente del tiempo que pasó como [alt_name]? ¿Fue por el shock del momento, o...?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2892
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_75fadc0a:

    # "Or can she really not remember at all? If she stuck around instead of fleeing, maybe we could've found out together."
    "¿O de verdad no puede recordar? Si se hubiera quedado en lugar de huir, tal vez lo habríamos averiguado juntos."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2906
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_bf8185ec:

    # "She'll know I wasn't trying to do anything bad to her, and she'll want to talk to me again. She'll want to understand the reactions she's had to my hypnosis."
    "Sabrá que no intentaba hacerle nada malo, y querrá hablar conmigo otra vez. Querrá entender la reacción que tuvo hacia mi hipnosis."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2928
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_4436bdd0:

    # "As I head into class and take my seat, I'm reminded again of just how much I fucked up with her."
    "Al llegar a la clase y tomar asiento, me acuerdo una vez más de cuánto la cagué con ella."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2929
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_07be1472:

    # "Even if she knows I meant her no harm, if she still can't remember anything of her time as \"[alt_name]\"? "
    "Incluso si sabe que no tenía intención de causar daño, si aún no puede recordar nada del tiempo que pasó como \"[alt_name]\"..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2930
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a7865e69:

    # "That's gotta be a shock to the system to say the least."
    "Eso debe ser un gran impacto para su sistema, por lo menos."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2949
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_fab6b43f:

    # "If I could just talk to her and clear the air. Apologize. Find out how she's doing, at least..."
    "Si pudiera tan solo hablar con ella y aclarar las cosas. Disculparme. Al menos averiguar cómo se siente..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2956
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_93d6008b:

    # "But it seems she can't even stand to look at me..."
    "Pero parece que ni siquiera puede mirarme..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2971
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d418d3e8:

    # "I can only watch from my desk as Sayori hurriedly strolls ahead of the others to the door."
    "Solo puedo observar desde mi escritorio cómo Sayori se adelanta apresuradamente a los demás en dirección a la puerta."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2980
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_68b86fd5:

    # "I let out a pained sigh."
    "Dejo salir un acongojado suspiro."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2981
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2d00b75a:

    # ks sigh "I just want to tell her I'm sorry for how things turned out."
    ks sigh "Solo quiero decirle cuánto lo siento por lo que pasó."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2982
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b92271cf:

    # n side frown "Well maybe \"sorry\" isn't going to cut it right now after what you did to her." with dissolve
    n side frown "Tal vez un \"lo siento\" no será suficiente después de lo que le hiciste." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3011
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d985c1e6:

    # ks confused "At least tell me how she's doing. Why'd she involve you at all?"
    ks confused "Al menos dime cómo está. ¿Y por qué te involucró a ti?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3041
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_642d3eb0:

    # "But tomorrow I'll finally be able to talk to Sayori and figure out what the hell happened to her."
    "Pero mañana finalmente podré hablar con Sayori y averiguar qué diablos le ocurrió."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3042
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_64ff564a:

    # "Figure out how badly I screwed up?"
    "¿Averiguar qué tan profundo metí la pata?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3043
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9e415118:

    # "I mean sure, hypnosis can't force someone to do things they don't want to do. Pretty much everything I read on it confirmed that was the case."
    "Digo, claro, la hipnosis no puede obligar a alguien a hacer cosas que no quiera. Básicamente todo lo que leo lo confirma."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3044
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_16df0c9e:

    # "But even so, I've also read how it can lower a person's inhibitions. Convince them to maybe go a little further than they meant to."
    "Sin embargo, también leí que puede reducir la inhibición de la gente. Convencerla de tal vez ir un poco más lejos de que normalmente haría."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3050
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_5e4cb232:

    # "Sayori was nervous about this whole deal, but she went along with it for my sake."
    "Sayori estaba nerviosa con todo esto, pero aceptó hacerlo por mí."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3051
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_97dce551:

    # "And yeah, she did come around to it in a big way, more than she ever thought she would."
    "Y sí, vaya que lo hizo en grande, más de lo que jamás imaginé."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3052
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_fa3bfa44:

    # "But it was supposed to be just a little trick for my hypnosis show. And a trick is supposed to end when the show's over."
    "Pero se suponía que fuera un simple truco para mi acto de hipnosis. Y un truco debe terminar cuando termina el espectáculo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3053
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_c3e52b43:

    # "I REALLY should've told her to go back to normal before I let her leave last night."
    "REALMENTE debí decirle que volviera a la normalidad antes de dejarla ir anoche."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3056
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_08e04dbc:

    # "But it's too late to think about what I should've done. I can only hope Sayori can forgive me for it, and give me a chance to set things right."
    "Pero es muy tarde para pensar en lo que debí haber hecho. Solo puedo esperar que Sayori pueda perdonarme por ello, y darme una oportunidad de arreglar las cosas."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:3057
translate spanish Day5_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_25f90a54:

    # "Sayori's a logical person, after all. So if I can just sit down with her and explain everything rationally, I'm sure she'll come around..."
    "Sayori es una persona lógica, después de todo. Así que, si puedo sentarme con ella y explicar todo de forma racional, estoy seguro de que entenderá..."

