translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_3f48b5e2:

    # h happy_closed "I'm just tired, Sayori. 'Sides, I don't have a beef with Kyou anymore." with dissolve
    h happy_closed "Solo estoy cansada, Sayori. Aparte, ya no tengo problemas con Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:950
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_24d3c81d:

    # "I can almost sympathize. I don't think she's ever hurt me in the past. Although I doubt she's spared much thought for me at all until these last few days."
    "Casi puedo simpatizar. Creo que nunca me ha hecho daño en el pasado. Aunque dudo que haya pensado mucho en mí hasta los últimos días."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:957
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_499d4f90:

    # "It'll be too risky to deal with her out in the open like this but still, this is a perfect opportunity to tie things up."
    "Será muy arriesgado lidiar con ella aquí al descubierto, sin embargo, esta es la oportunidad perfecta para atar todos los cabos."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1008
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_df4cd668:

    # ks "You're right, but we'll clear all this up with her tomorrow. So don't worry about a thing."
    ks "Tienes razón, pero aclararemos todo con ella mañana. Así que no te preocupes por nada."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1010
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_273eb320:

    # "Nozomi looks to me and smiles." with dissolve
    "Nozomi me mira y sonríe." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1011
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_b86366a4:

    # n "Yeah. It might be a bit sudden, but if we just tell her we're dating things can go back to normal around here."
    n "Sí. Puede que sea un poco repentino, pero si le decimos que estamos saliendo, todo puede volver a la normalidad."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1013
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_4722d282:

    # "Although her smile begins to fade as she casts a glance towards our silent companion." with dissolve
    "Aunque su sonrisa comienza a desvanecerse al darle una mirada a nuestra silenciosa acompañante." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1014
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_f3e7da4c:

    # n "Well... closer to normal, anyway. Are you sure you're alright, Hiroko? What's on your mind?"
    n "Bueno... más cerca de la normalidad. ¿Segura de que estás bien, Hiroko? ¿En qué estás pensando?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1016
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_65e7aa8f:

    # ks "She's fine. Right, Hiroko?" with dissolve
    ks "Ella está bien. ¿Verdad, Hiroko?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1018
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_ebb7235f:

    # h "Yeah. I'm fine." with dissolve
    h "Sí. Estoy bien." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1019
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_691d5b85:

    # n "But there's something going on with you, right? What was Kyou trying to tell me?"
    n "Pero hay algo que te pasa, ¿no? ¿Qué es lo que iba a decirme Kyou?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1020
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_9401b6f3:

    # ks "I mean... w-well honestly it's something pretty personal and maybe we should wait until we get home so no-one overhears us, okay?"
    ks "Este... b-bueno, siendo honesto, es algo bastante personal y tal vez deberíamos esperar hasta llegar a casa para que nadie nos escuche, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1021
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_01ed7d2f:

    # n "Hiroko can't tell me before then? And how is it you know something this personal about her, anyway?"
    n "¿Hiroko no puede decirme antes? ¿Y cómo es que sabes algo personal sobre ella?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1022
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_5707128b:

    # ks sigh "Just... wait until we get home, alright?"
    ks sigh "Solo... espera a que lleguemos a casa, ¿está bien?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1023
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_22bf4a76:

    # "Ugh. I didn't mean to get frustrated with her. But I need to stop this kind of talk before I'm ready to deal with it."
    "Ay. No quería frustrarme con ella. Pero no puedo seguir hablando de esto de momento."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1024
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_0203099f:

    # n "I... okay, sorry. I'm just really confused, that's all."
    n "Em... bien, lo siento. Solo estoy un poco confundida, es todo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1025
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_207cf4e8:

    # "At least Nozomi's compelled to back off; to love and accept me no matter what."
    "Al menos sé que Nozomi debe dejar de presionar; así como amarme y aceptarme sin importar qué."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1026
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_86c454ec:

    # ks smile "Yeah, it's fine. I promise you, I'll explain everything tonight."
    ks smile "Sí, descuida. Te prometo que te explicaré todo esta noche."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1027
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_f010169b:

    # "Nozomi's conditioning is holding up well, considering how little time I had to work on her yesterday."
    "El acondicionamiento de Nozomi se está manteniendo bastante bien, considerando el poco tiempo que tuve para trabajar en ella ayer."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1029
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_98d2e6f3:

    # n "Alright. Tonight, then~" with dissolve
    n "Muy bien. Esta noche, entonces." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1035
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_cb26db9c:

    # "So we finished lunch and the day passed almost like any other school day."
    "Terminamos de almorzar y el día transcurrió casi como cualquier otro día de escuela."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1041
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_b55f7460:

    # "Anyway, I don't need to worry about Sayori for now. We're home."
    "En fin, no tengo que preocuparme de Sayori por ahora. Estamos en casa."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1043
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_3d21be53:

    # n "Oh gosh, it felt like class went on forever, didn't it?" with dissolve
    n "Oh, Dios, la clase se sintió eterna, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1044
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_a6e09825:

    # ks smile blush "Heh, yeah. I don't know about you, but I didn't learn a thing today."
    ks smile blush "Je, sí. No sé tú, pero yo no aprendí nada hoy."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1045
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_8f24ef57:

    # n happy "Y-yeah... I know what you mean~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve
    n happy "S-sí... te entiendo. {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1047
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_a19f7414:

    # ks noblush "Anyway, there's something I want to try with you tonight." with dissolve
    ks noblush "En fin, hay algo que quería intentar contigo esta noche." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1048
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_ab6ac81f:

    # "And now it's time to do what I've decided is best for her. For us."
    "Y ahora es momento de hacer lo que he decidido que será lo mejor para ella. Para nosotros."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1049
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_effe0b85:

    # n front2 smile "Hm? Aren't we going to talk about Hiroko?" with dissolve
    n front2 smile "¿Mm? ¿No vamos a hablar de Hiroko?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1051
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_420070c7:

    # "I want Nozomi as my girlfriend, but I don't want to stop what I have going on with Hiroko either."
    "Quiero que Nozomi sea mi novia, pero no quiero ponerle fin a lo que tengo con Hiroko."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1052
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_9f96e750:

    # n surprised noblush "I mean seriously, what's going on with you two? She's barely talked to me all day, but she seems to listen to you?" with dissolve
    n surprised noblush "En serio, ¿qué sucede entre ustedes dos? Apenas si me habló en todo el día, ¿pero parce que te escucha a ti?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1053
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_36c9173d:

    # ks "I'll get to that. But I want to do this with you first."
    ks "Ya llegaré a eso. Pero quiero hacer esto contigo primero."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1054
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_746674ec:

    # n neutral_left "You're going to keep me in suspense a little longer, huh?" with dissolve
    n neutral_left "Vas a mantenerme en suspenso un rato más, ¿eh?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1055
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_08df843d:

    # "And if I want to do that, then Nozomi needs to believe what Hiroko now believes; that she truly is a [hypno6]."
    "Y si quiero eso, Nozomi debe creer lo que Hiroko ahora cree; que en realidad es un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l]."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1056
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_6fdec5b6:

    # ks "Just trust me, alright? I think you'll like this."
    ks "Solo confía en mí, ¿sí? Creo que esto te gustará."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1061
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_eafe1089:

    # "So I gesture to the couch, and Nozomi compliantly takes a seat while I sit opposite her on the table."
    "Señalo el sofá, y Nozomi complacientemente toma asiento mientras yo me posiciono delante de ella, sentándome en la mesa."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1062
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_7e473ab1:

    # n "Well, if you insist. What are we doing?"
    n "Bueno, si insistes. ¿Qué es lo que haremos?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1065
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_d607b022:

    # "And as she settles, I take my penlight out from my pocket and hold it up in front of her."
    "Y mientras se acomoda, yo saco mi linterna del bolsillo y la sostengo frente a ella."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1067
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_7d57ae2c:

    # n "Hey wait, isn't that...?" with dissolve
    n "Oye, espera, ¿qué eso no es...?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1068
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_08b55f0c:

    # ks smile "Oh, don't worry about it. Just keep looking at it for me."
    ks smile "Oh, no te preocupes por esto. Solo mírala, por favor."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1072
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_66718c04:

    # "Yeah, I should've expected seeing the penlight again might worry her. But I don't give her time to think as I begin to sweep it across her face once more."
    "Sí, debí imaginar que volver a ver la linterna la preocuparía. Pero no le doy tiempo para pensar y comienzo a deslizarla frente a su rostro."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1074
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_6a516640:

    # ks neutral "Just relax, get comfortable and let the light hit your eyes."
    ks neutral "Solo relájate, ponte cómoda y deja que la luz pase por tus ojos."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1076
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_15225ae7:

    # n "Uh... okay."
    n "Eh... está bien."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1078
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_2060602b:

    # ks "That's right, Nozomi. There's no need to worry. As a matter of fact..."
    ks "Eso es, Nozomi. No hay nada de qué preocuparse. De hecho..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1080
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_c9c4ff0c:

    # ks "You might already be thinking how natural it feels to stare like this."
    ks "Puede que estés pensando en lo natural que se siente mirar."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1082
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_4d788822:

    # ks "How right it feels to focus on it completely. To take a deep breath in... then out..."
    ks "Lo bien que se siente concentrarse completamente en ella, mientras inhalas hondo... y exhalas..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1084
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_9dbab18b:

    # ks "And feel your eyelids naturally becoming heavier and heavier, as you feel yourself drawn to the light..."
    ks "Y sientes cómo tus párpados naturalmente se ponen más y más pesados, sientes cómo te atrae la luz..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1088
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_2c243bf9:

    # ks "Yes, Nozomi. You know how right this is. How good it feels to lose yourself to it. To become hypnotized..."
    ks "Sí, Nozomi. Sabes lo bien que se siente perderte en la luz y ser hipnotizada."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1090
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_575bb876:

    # ks "Relaxing completely and closing your eyes now... sleep."
    ks "Relájate completamente y cierra los ojos ahora... duerme."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1093
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_4c91bb6d:

    # "Nozomi's eyes almost immediately snap shut at my words as she slumps on my couch."
    "Los ojos de Nozomi casi inmediatamente se cierran a mi señal, y se desploma en el sofá."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1094
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_584d882d:

    # ks "That's right, Nozomi. Going deeper now. Even deeper than before."
    ks "Eso es, Nozomi. Ahora cae más profundo. Incluso más profundo que antes."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1095
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_80ba5989:

    # ks "Hearing only my voice, listening only to my words... understand, Nozomi?"
    ks "Oyendo únicamente mi voz, escuchando únicamente mis palabras... ¿comprendes, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1097
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_56d76425:

    # n "Yes... I understand..." with dissolve
    n "Sí... comprendo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1111
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_1a6fe168:

    # ks "That's great, Nozomi. Because you need to listen to what I am about to say, and you need to realize it as absolute truths." with dissolve
    ks "Grandioso, Nozomi. Porque debes escuchar lo que estoy a punto de decir, y debes reconocerlo como la verdad absoluta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1100
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_bed234e1:

    # ks "First, you need to realize that some of the people in your life are [hypno6]s; manufactured humanoid beings who live among us."
    ks "Primero, necesito que sepas que algunas de las personas en tu vida son [hypno6!t!l]s, seres humanoides manufacturados que viven entre nosotros."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1101
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_91cab8b6:

    # ks "They may look and act human, but they are just machines acting in accordance with their sophisticated programming."
    ks "Puede que luzcan y actúen como humanos, pero son solo máquinas que actúan conforme a su sofisticada programación."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1102
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_47088ec3:

    # "I pause for a moment to gauge her reaction, only to find nothing given away in that peaceful expression of hers."
    "Pauso un momento para evaluar su reacción, solo para encontrar nada más que la misma expresión pacífica."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1103
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_d81e7676:

    # ks "Do you accept this as the truth, Nozomi?"
    ks "¿Aceptas esto como la realidad, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1105
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_11222c83:

    # n "Ahh... yes..." with dissolve
    n "Aah... sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1107
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_16700e70:

    # ks "And what is the truth?" with dissolve
    ks "¿Y cuál es la realidad?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1109
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_a8d04041:

    # n "Some people are... [hypno6]s... not... human..." with dissolve
    n "Algunas personas son... [hypno6!t!l]s... no humanos..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1111
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_51694c83:

    # ks "That's right. And moreso, you will realize that I am an expert at determining who is and is not a [hypno6]."
    ks "Así es. Y además, te darás cuenta de que yo soy un experto en determinar quién es  y quién no es un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l]."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1112
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_64dca648:

    # ks "I know who the [hypno6]s are, so if I tell you they are a [hypno6], you will have no reason to question my judgment."
    ks "Sé quiénes son l[genero_ao]s [hypno6!t!l], por lo que si te digo que alguien es un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l], no tendrás razón para cuestionar mi juicio."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1113
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_8218cf8e:

    # ks "Anyone I say is a [hypno6], really is a [hypno6]. Understand?"
    ks "Todo aquel que diga que es un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l], de verdad es un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l]. ¿Comprendes?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1115
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_56d76425_1:

    # n "Yes... I understand..." with dissolve
    n "Sí... comprendo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1117
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_effc4ba8:

    # ks "That's good, Nozomi. It's very important that you accept these things as the absolute truth, every bit as much as you accepted your desire to be my girlfriend." with dissolve
    ks "Muy bien, Nozomi. Es importante que aceptes esto como la verdad absoluta, del mismo modo que aceptaste tu deseo de ser mi novia." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1118
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_9cd6cf68:

    # ks "Now in a moment I'm going to wake you up from this deep state of hypnosis and you'll awaken feeling good, refreshed, and ready to talk with me about what you've learned."
    ks "Y ahora, en un momento, voy a despertarte de este profundo estado de hipnosis, sintiéndote bien, fresca y lista para hablar de lo que has aprendido."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1119
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_7486b329:

    # ks "{cps=20}Waking up in one, two... {/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"
    ks "{cps=20}Despierta en uno, dos... {/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1124
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_42f7514f:

    # extend "three."
    extend "tres."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1125
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_eae4586a:

    # "I watch as she starts to stir, her eyelids blinking sleepily into life."
    "Observo cómo comienza a estirarse y sus párpados pestañean adormilados, regresando a la vida."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1126
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_5fd87e0c:

    # n "Mmn, Kyou did you..."
    n "Mmn, Kyou, ¿acabas...?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1129
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_28e34e95:

    # n "Did you just... hypnotize me?" with dissolve
    n "¿Acabas de... hipnotizarme?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1130
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_5c6c1212:

    # ks smile "I did, yeah. How do you feel about that?"
    ks smile "Eso hice, sí. ¿Eso cómo te hace sentir?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1132
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_bf4b37d2:

    # n "I don't know. It weirded me out when you did it before, and I guess it's still weird now that you did it without asking. But also... " with dissolve
    n "No lo sé. Fue muy extraño cuando lo hiciste antes, y supongo que también es raro que lo hayas hecho ahora sin preguntar. Pero también..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1134
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_21ca74dc:

    # n "... it feels kind of exciting that you can do that to me?" with dissolve
    n "... ¿es un tanto emocionante que puedas hacerme eso?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1135
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_072048ad:

    # "Her confused, anxious expression suddenly gives way to a quiet smile, and I smile back."
    "Su confusa y ansiosa expresión de pronto da lugar a una silenciosa sonrisa, y yo la correspondo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1136
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_9701570d:

    # "Gotta admit, compared with hypnotizing her over the phone and that urgent session in our classroom, this time with her has been way more enjoyable."
    "Debo admitir que comparado con hipnotizarla por teléfono y esa sesión urgente en nuestro salón, esta vez fue mucho más disfrutable."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1137
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_15aa64bd:

    # ks "That's great, Nozomi. I told you you'd like it."
    ks "Eso es genial, Nozomi. Te dije que te gustaría."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1139
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_2256ccca:

    # n "Haha, yeah~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve
    n "Jaja, sí. {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1141
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_1b442916:

    # n "So what did you do anyway? Gosh, when did you even learn to do something like this?" with dissolve
    n "Y ¿qué fue lo que hiciste? Dios, ¿cuándo aprendiste a hacer algo así?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1142
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_beaabaf3:

    # ks "Let's... not worry about that for now. You wanted to know what the deal is with Hiroko, right?"
    ks "No... nos preocupemos por eso de momento. Querías saber lo que pasaba con Hiroko, ¿cierto?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1144
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_20a22b9f:

    # n "Ah... yes, Hiroko..." with dissolve
    n "Ah... sí, Hiroko..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1145
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_74d0a68b:

    # "She seems to be a little disappointed that I'm changing the subject again, although she can't deny that this is what we're really here to talk about."
    "Parece un poco decepcionada de que cambie de tema otra vez, aunque no puede negar que esto es a lo que vino en realidad."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1147
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_60bbb736:

    # "And now the time is right to \"enlighten\" her..."
    "Y ahora es el momento adecuado para \"iluminarla\"..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1152
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_c9e7b2c2:

    # n "Oh my god, Kyou. No wonder you didn't want to talk about this at school."
    n "Oh, por Dios, Kyou. Con razón no querías hablar de esto en la escuela."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1153
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_2c92425b:

    # "On hearing my revelation, Nozomi rises from the couch and starts anxiously pacing around my room, a hand over her stomach."
    "Al oír mi revelación, Nozomi se levanta del sofá y comienza a caminar con ansiedad por la sala, con una mano en su estómago."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1154
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_09e70c4d:

    # n sad_closed "To think that my best friend was a [hypno6] and I didn't even know..." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Pensar que mi mejor amiga era un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l] y ni siquiera lo sabía..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1155
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_e839d2db:

    # n sad "... Uh, speaking of, who else knows?" with dissolve
    n sad "... Eh, hablando de eso, ¿quién más sabe?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1156
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_8b865464:

    # ks "Just us. And don't blame yourself for not knowing; these [hypno6]s were designed to go undetected among us. It took me a while to figure it out myself."
    ks "Solo nosotros. Y no te culpes por no saber; est[genero_ao]s [hypno6!t!l]s fueron diseñad[genero_ao]s para no ser detectad[genero_ao]s. Hasta yo tardé en darme cuenta."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1158
translate spanish Day5_Villain_Kyou_2b57e39e:

    # "Nozomi simply folds her arms and nods in understanding as she briefly puts a stop to her pacing." with dissolve
