translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_fdf92141:

    # "Well, she's on time and she didn't acknowledge me at all. I guess that's a good sign."
    "Bueno, llegó a tiempo y ni siquiera miró en mi dirección. Supongo que eso es una buena señal."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1445
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_ddaeae49:

    # "But then, suppose Akiko really did blow her cover. What could Nozomi even do about it?"
    "Pero claro, suponiendo que Akiko hubiera hablado de más. ¿Qué podría hacer Nozomi al respecto?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1448
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_44f22c25:

    # "My pondering continues through the morning, when eventually the school bell once more rings to announce the start of lunch break."
    "Continúo pensando en eso toda la mañana, cuando eventualmente suena una vez más la campana para anunciar el inicio del almuerzo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1454
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_57d71166:

    # n "Alright. Well, up we go then." with dissolve
    n "Muy bien. Pues, vamos arriba." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1455
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_2d3de8bb:

    # "And I can tell Nozomi still isn't giving anything away."
    "Y puedo notar que Nozomi sigue sin dar ninguna pista."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1456
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_53aa6ca0:

    # h sad_side "I mean, if you wanna? We don't have to." with dissolve
    h sad_side "Bueno, solo si quieres. No estás obligada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1457
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_6951069b:

    # s uniform_handup sleeptalk "That's right. We do have options, Nozomi." with dissolve
    s uniform_handup sleeptalk "Es cierto. Tenemos opciones, Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1458
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_1ca47f87:

    # s frown_right "After all, we know he won't remain here for much longer." with dissolve
    s frown_right "Después de todo, sabemos que él no se quedará aquí por mucho tiempo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1460
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_fb214963:

    # h frown "Uh-huh..." with dissolve
    h frown "Ajá..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1461
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_c417eb35:

    # "Christ. I'm leaving you girls alone and you still think you can bully me."
    "Dios. ¿Las estoy dejando en paz y creen que aún pueden hostigarme?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1463
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_63a96053:

    # "Well, fine. Be that way. I don't really care about Nozomi and you bitches anyway."
    "Bueno, actúen así si quieren. No me importan ni Nozomi ni ustedes, perras, de todos modos."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1464
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_111eecd7:

    # a "Kyou! Good afternoon~"
    a "¡Kyou! Buenas tardes."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1466
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_34e6495e:

    # "There's only one girl I want to be around right now." with dissolve
    "Solo hay una chica junto a la que quiero estar ahora mismo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1467
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_bd37a234:

    # ks smile "Noz-... Akiko. Just the girl I've been dying to see."
    ks smile "Noz-... Akiko. Justo la chica a la que me moría por ver."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1468
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_c997771f:

    # "Goddammit. I slipped up right in front of her, and there's no way she didn't notice."
    "Maldita sea. Me equivoqué delante de ella, y casi seguro lo notó."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1469
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_93fd5807:

    # a happy "Mhmhmhm~" with dissolve
    a happy "Jijiji." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1471
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_80f6fe9c:

    # "Obviously I still have both girls in my mind. I was practically helpless to stop Nozomi's name from just dropping off my tongue like that."
    "Obviamente aún tengo a ambas chicas en mi mente. Prácticamente no pude hacer nada para evitar que el nombre de Nozomi escapara de mi boca así."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1472
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_791f3252:

    # a smile "It's good to see you too, Kyou. Let's talk inside, okay?" with dissolve
    a smile "Es bueno verte, Kyou. Hablemos adentro, ¿sí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1473
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_7e8ea960:

    # "Come to think of it, I've often heard Nozomi giggle just like that when she's around her friends."
    "Ahora que lo pienso, he escuchado con frecuencia a Nozomi reírse justo así cuando está con sus amigas."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1474
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_a061e366:

    # ks "Y... yeah."
    ks "S... sí."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1479
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_d11b904f:

    # "It's only been a moment, but the way Akiko's carrying herself just seems different today."
    "Solo ha pasado un momento, pero los movimientos y los gestos de Akiko perecen diferentes hoy."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1480
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_6f9aaff5:

    # "So her talk with Nozomi went that well? Did she really pick up that much from Nozomi last night?"
    "¿O sea que su charla con Nozomi salió bien? ¿De verdad aprendió tanto de Nozomi anoche?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1484
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_4da21abc:

    # a "Now Kyou, before you say anything else, I just wanted to say thank you for giving me the push I needed to talk to Nozomi last night." with dissolve
    a "Ahora, Kyou, antes de que digas nada, quería agradecerte por darme el empujón que necesitaba para hablar con Nozomi anoche." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1485
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_fcfcf719:

    # "I am... fascinated."
    "Estoy... fascinado."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1486
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_dd5ff3d5:

    # ks smile "Oh... yeah. No problem, Akiko."
    ks smile "Oh... Sí. No hay problema, Akiko."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1487
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_f1eb87b3:

    # a happy blush "Gosh, I had such a great time catching up with her~" with dissolve
    a happy blush "Cielos, me la pasé genial poniéndome al día con ella." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1488
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_21c3e236:

    # ks "You gotta tell me all about it."
    ks "Tienes que contármelo todo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1489
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_61ab10e2:

    # a smile "Okay, so we met up after club and she took us to this quaint little café a few blocks away." with dissolve
    a smile "Muy bien, bueno, nos reunimos después del club y nos llevó a un pintoresco café a unas cuadras." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1490
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_be0ee5dd:

    # a neutral -blush "And when we got there... well, we started off by talking about you, of course. It's the reason I reached out to her, after all." with dissolve
    a neutral -blush "Y cuando llegamos ahí... bueno, empezamos hablando sobre ti, por supuesto. Es la razón por la que me acerqué a ella, después de todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1491
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_5249c697:

    # ks neutral "Yeah. Of course."
    ks neutral "Sí. Por supuesto."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1492
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_c14e4f97:

    # a neutral_side "I won't tell you everything she said, but she did appreciate that someone else was trying to do anything about her... her situation." with dissolve
    a neutral_side "No te diré todo lo que dijo, pero apreció que alguien más intentara hacer algo por su... su situación." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1493
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_e4d3cd89:

    # a sleeptalk "Only that it shouldn't be down to \"us students\" to handle such matters." with dissolve
    a sleeptalk "Aunque dijo que no debería depender de \"nosotros los estudiantes\" manejar tales asuntos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1494
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_8b4e569a:

    # a sad_side "In other words, she's still worried about you. And me, for that matter." with dissolve
    a sad_side "En otras palabras, aún le causas preocupación. Y yo también, de hecho." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1495
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_12c1ea87:

    # "I simply nod. This is hardly news to me, after all. But I let her continue."
    "Simplemente le asiento. Esto no son novedades para mí, después de todo. Pero dejo que continúe."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1496
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_72b3a872:

    # a neutral "She certainly doesn't think we should be doing this, but she sorta backed down a little when I mentioned my interest in becoming a therapist when I graduate." with dissolve
    a neutral "Ciertamente no cree que debamos estar haciendo esto, pareció al menos entenderlo un poco más cuando le mencioné mi interés en volverme terapeuta al graduarme." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1497
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_0aafee36:

    # a uniform_down2 armband_down sleeptalk "And you were right to suggest I not mention that you hypnotized me. She did ask, and I knew she wouldn't take it well if I told her." with dissolve
    a uniform_down2 armband_down sleeptalk "Y tuviste razón en sugerir que no mencionara que me hipnotizaste. Me preguntó, y yo sabía que no se lo tomaría bien si le contaba." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1498
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_1c7c4899:

    # ks confused "Yeah... So what *did* you tell her?"
    ks confused "Sí... ¿Y qué le contaste?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1499
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_9b8b251a:

    # a neutral "Obviously I tried to speak up for you. You've been nothing but a gentleman to me, and I told her that you seem a lot calmer since we started talking." with dissolve
    a neutral "Obviamente intenté defenderte. No has sido más que un caballero conmigo, y le dije que pareces mucho más calmado desde que comenzamos a hablar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1500
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_98b6a15b:

    # a neutral_side "I told her we mostly made smalltalk about school, and that you appreciated having a tranquil space to spend lunch in, away from your classmates." with dissolve
    a neutral_side "Le dije que más que nada charlamos sobre la escuela, y que apreciabas tener un espacio tranquilo en el cual pasar el almuerzo, lejos de tus compañeros." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1501
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_d28fe784:

    # a sleeptalk "She seemed content, but it was obvious she doesn't like the idea of you being alone with a girl for an hour, no matter how much I told her I was happy to be here." with dissolve
    a sleeptalk "Parecía conforme, pero era obvio que no le gusta la idea de que estés solo con una chica por una hora, sin importar cuánto le dije que estaba feliz de estar aquí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1502
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_58893fa1:

    # a sad "She obviously still thinks you're a danger." with dissolve
    a sad "Es evidente que aún cree que ere un peligro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1503
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_3a0b95e0:

    # "Again, I'm not surprised Nozomi still believes I'm a shit. But it's nice thinking at least my student council president's fighting my corner, even if I did put her up to it."
    "De nuevo, no me sorprende que Nozomi aún me crea una mierda. Pero es lindo pensar que al menos la presidenta está peleando en mi esquina, aunque yo la haya puesto ahí."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1504
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_72c03e30:

    # ks neutral "That can't have been all you talked about, though. You said you had a great time?"
    ks neutral "Aunque eso no puede ser todo de lo que hablaron. ¿Dijiste que la pasaste genial?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1505
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_aede8eb1:

    # a uniform2 armband happy "Mhm!" with dissolve
    a uniform2 armband happy "¡Mjm!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1506
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_cdd8dd0f:

    # "Akiko instantly perks up and claps her hands together, now that the serious business is behind us."
    "Akiko instantáneamente se anima y junta sus manos, ahora que la parte seria quedó atrás."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1507
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_01b4a3dc:

    # a smile "When we reached this sorta impasse about you, I tried to cheer her up. I told her I wanted to get to know her more as a person, tell me more about herself." with dissolve
    a smile "Cuando llegamos a un punto muerto sobre ti, intenté subirle el ánimo. Le dije que quería conocerla más como persona, y que me hablara de ella." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1508
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_fadc5a57:

    # a uniform_up2 armband_up smile_side "No surprise that our literature club president reads a lot of books. I happen to read plenty myself, so we had a few recommendations for each other." with dissolve
    a uniform_up2 armband_up smile_side "No es sorpresa que la presidenta del club de literatura lea muchos libros. Yo también leo bastantes, así que intercambiamos recomendaciones." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1509
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_7daa6fe0:

    # a smile "I talked about my kendo practice, and she was gushing to me about board games... she was so passionate about them she practically made an instant fan out of me!" with dissolve
    a smile "Hablé sobre mi práctica de kendo, y ella no paraba de hablar sobre juegos de mesa... ¡la apasionan tanto que prácticamente me volvió una fan al instante!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1510
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_3eb86e35:

    # a laugh "She even said she'd invite me to her next game night! How cool is that?" with dissolve
    a laugh "¡Incluso me dijo que me invitaría a su próxima noche de juegos! ¿No es grandioso?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1511
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_05df9abe:

    # ks smile "Oh. So you think you'll start hanging out with her more after this?"
    ks smile "Oh. Entonces, ¿crees que pasarás más tiempo con ella después de esto?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1512
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_71a7d98c:

    # a smile blush "Y-yeah! I mean, if she wants? I really hope she wants to." with dissolve
    a smile blush "¡S-sí! Digo, si ella quiere. De verdad espero que quiera." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1513
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_955f1ac2:

    # a happy "I... I-I really think we could be the best of friends~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve
    a happy "De... de verdad creo que podríamos ser las mejores amigas que hay. {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1514
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_85cb4e9e:

    # "That's cute, but more importantly, it seems everything went without a hitch. Akiko learned a lot from Nozomi last night."
    "Qué ternura, pero más importante, parece que todo fue sobre ruedas. Akiko aprendió mucho de Nozomi anoche."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1515
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_c880ef47:

    # "There's just one little wrinkle."
    "Solo hay un pequeño detalle."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1517
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_20c1b116:

    # ks smile "You could. But I was thinking, now that the weekend's coming up..." with dissolve
    ks smile "Apuesto a que sí. Pero estaba pensando, ahora que el fin de semana está por llegar..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1518
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_5cd04a64:

    # "I want her to hang out more with me."
    "Quiero que pase más tiempo conmigo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1519
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_52247d7c:

    # ks "... How do you feel about meeting up tomorrow?"
    ks "... ¿Qué te parecería vernos mañana?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1520
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_2fa55b89:

    # a surprised "Um... r-really? I..." with dissolve
    a surprised "Em... ¿d-de verdad? Yo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1521
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_ff418f7d:

    # a smile "Well, I guess I could make that work. I wasn't planning on going to kendo practice tomorrow anyway." with dissolve
    a smile "Bueno, supongo que podría arreglármelas. No planeaba ir a práctica de kendo mañana de todos modos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1522
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_6d275cf0:

    # ks confused "Oh? What were you planning on doing then?"
    ks confused "¿Oh? ¿Qué planeas hacer, entonces?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1523
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_4f08fe0e:

    # a smile_side "I... {w=2.0}{nw}" with dissolve
    a smile_side "Pues... {w=2.0}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1526
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_131a75d3:

    # extend "ehehehehe~"
    extend " ejejejeje."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1527
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_bab9a39a:

    # "Oh now, that's an interesting reaction."
    "Oh, qué interesante reacción."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1528
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_c7ee6a64:

    # ks smile "What?"
    ks smile "¿Qué?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1529
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_5532612d:

    # a smile "I, um... n-need to go into town; there's a couple of appointments I need to get to. But I can fit you in if you don't mind meeting me there." with dissolve
    a smile "Bueno, em... n-necesito ir a la ciudad; hay un par de lugares a los que agendé una cita. Pero puedo invitarte si no te molesta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1530
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_24f983a1:

    # "Very interesting."
    "Muy interesante."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1531
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_fb5641fd:

    # ks "Sure, I don't mind at all."
    ks "Claro, no me molesta para nada."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1532
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_fe805d82:

    # a uniform_down2 armband_down "Just promise me one thing, okay?" with dissolve
    a uniform_down2 armband_down "Solo prométeme una cosa, ¿sí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1533
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_21ce92c3:

    # ks confused "What's that?"
    ks confused "¿Qué cosa?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1534
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_19957bc4:

    # a smile_side "I-it's gonna sound so silly..." with dissolve
    a smile_side "S-sonará muy tonto..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1535
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_34068ec2:

    # ks "No, come on, just tell me!"
    ks "¡No, vamos, solo dime!"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1537
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_a3dbcb04:

    # a "When... when we see each other tomorrow..."
    a "Cuando... cuando nos veamos mañana..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1538
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_72f4af93:

    # a shy "C-could you call me... Nozomi?" with dissolve
    a shy "¿P-podrías llamarme... Nozomi?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1540
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_0615e285:

    # "((AUTHOR'S NOTE: And that's as far as we get this time~ ))"
    "(( NOTA DE LA AUTORA: Y hasta aquí llegamos esta vez. ))"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1541
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_0350d0ca:

    # "(( Please look forward to the next update, where I'll be developing this story further. Stay tuned! ))"
    "(( Por favor, esperen con ansias la próxima actualización, donde continuaré desarrollando esta historia! ¡Manténganse en sintonía! ))"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:1542
translate spanish Day5_Villain2_Kyou_a08c132c:

    # "{size=30}TO BE CONTINUED...{/size}"
    "{size=30}CONTINUARÁ...{/size}"
