    extend "MIERDA, ¿qué me hiciste esta vez?" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4450
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_244096ce:

    # "Heh. I was waiting for her to get up to speed. Seems she's all caught up now."
    "Je. Estaba esperando a que recobrara el ritmo. Parece que ya se recuperó."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4452
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_652afd57:

    # ks smirk "When you got here you were all about trying to renege on our arrangement, whining about \"payback\" and all. I just made sure you understand nothing's changed."
    ks smirk "Cuando viniste aquí, básicamente te habías rendido. Pero ahora ambos sabemos que jugarás como una campeona este fin de semana."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4455
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_6ff562da:

    # ks smirk "When you got here tonight you'd pretty much given up. But now we both know you're going to play like a champion this weekend."
    ks smirk "Cuando viniste aquí, básicamente te habías rendido. Pero ahora ambos sabemos que jugarás como una campeona este fin de semana."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4456
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_07e932da:

    # ks "And if you do your part, we'll both get what we want out of it. Isn't that great?"
    ks "Y si haces tu parte, ambos obtendremos lo que queremos. ¿No es grandioso?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4484
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_27b92364:

    # h "RRRRRRRAAAAARGH!" with shake
    h "¡GRRRRRRRAAAAARGH!" with shake

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4487
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_e870de19:

    # h irritated "WHY YOU GOTTA DO THIS TO ME?! HUH?!" with vpunch
    h irritated "¡¿POR QUÉ TIENES QUE HACERME ESTO?! ¡¿EH?!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4488
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_e2bb3978:

    # "No longer tethered by a compulsion to be hypnotized, Hiroko heaves herself off the couch and rages in front of me."
    "Sin estar ya atada por el impulso de ser hipnotizada, Hiroko se levanta del sofá se enfurece frente a mí."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4489
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_ad5c15a7:

    # "But I don't know, it seems a little half-hearted. Like she knows I might have even done her a favour here after how despondent she was."
    "Pero no sé, no parece del todo sincero. Como si supiera que puede que sí le haya hecho un favor luego de lo abatida que estaba."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4490
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_08e15a25:

    # ks smirk "Hey, if you don't want to do my little hypno show that bad, you can always throw the last game."
    ks smirk "Oye, si en serio no quieres hacer mi pequeño acto de hipnosis, siempre puedes perder el último juego."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4491
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_f1316325:

    # ks "Just something to think about."
    ks "Solo algo en qué pensar."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4492
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_42862275:

    # h furious "It ain't anything to think about, fuckface! How's it gonna look to everyone if I do that?" with dissolve
    h furious "¡No es nada en qué pensar, cabrón! ¿Qué pensarán todos si hago eso?" with dissolve

