    h uniform angry_side "Es que… {w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4497
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_6263dc3d:

    # extend irritated "RRRAAAAAARRRGH!" with shake
    extend irritated "¡GRRRAAAAAARRRGH!" with shake

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4503
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_1eba5c4e:

    # "Hiroko stamps her foot as she turns and stalks out of my house, growling and raging all the while."
    "Hiroko sale de mi casa, pisoteando con ira a cada paso."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4504
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_82bf1006:

    # ks "Good luck at the tournament!"
    ks "¡Buena suerte en el torneo!"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4508
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_eebf73bf:

    # "When my excitement cools off an hour later, I wonder whether giving Hiroko a way out of continuing this was really all that smart."
    "Cuando mi emoción se enfría una hora más tarde, me pregunto si darle a Hiroko una salida realmente fue inteligente."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4510
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_1e40b775:

    # "Why was I so confident she could win this tourney? Is she even that good of a player?"
    "¿Por qué tenía tanta confianza en que podía ganar el torneo? ¿Siquiera es una jugadora tan buena?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4511
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_0986f0cb:

    # "She did great against that friend of hers, sure, but what about the other schools? Don't they have better players than that?"
    "Lo hizo genial contra esa amiga suya, claro, pero ¿Qué hay de las chicas de las otras escuelas? ¿No tendrán mejores jugadoras?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4512
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_47fd77c9:

    # "I only gave Hiroko the attitude to win, but that's only gonna count for so much."
    "Solo le di a Hiroko la actitud para ganar, pero eso no lo va a ser todo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4513
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_c2b60457:

    # "How good is she really with her technique? Her strategy? Or... I dunno, whatever else a player needs?"
    "¿Qué tan buena es con su técnica? ¿Su estrategia? O... ¿Yo qué sé? ¿Lo que sea que necesite un jugador?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4514
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_ed8c2a23:

    # "Does it matter that she's so goddamned short? How many tennis champions are there under five feet tall?"
    "¿Importa que sea tan, pero tan enana? ¿Cuántas campeonas hay que midan metro y medio?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4515
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_38493a6b:

    # "Not to mention how badly I fucked up her match preparation. Shit, maybe I didn't think this through."
    "Sin mencionar cuánto jodí su preparación. Mierda, tal vez no lo pensé bien."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4516
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_119d9cbd:

    # "Still, though. I have to admit I'm a little excited about just how she'll behave in proper match conditions, knowing how she's taken to my hypnosis."
    "Aun así, no puedo decir que no me emociona descubrir cómo se comportará en un partido en condiciones adecuadas, sabiendo cuánto le ha funcionado mi hipnosis."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4520
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_bbda8071:

    # "Makes me want to see the effects for myself..."
    "Me hace querer ver los efectos por mi cuenta..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4531
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_252e284f:

    # "As much as I'm tempted... I'd better stop. Trying to make her conk out in class will probably attract a little too much attention."
    "Por tentado que esté... será mejor parar. Tratar de hacerla desmayarse en clase probablemente atraiga mucha atención."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4538
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_01afe1ee:

    # n "Cheer up, Hiroko. It's only a few more hours."
    n "Anímate, Hiroko. Solo unas cuantas horas más."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4539
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_b5d96c0c:

    # "Not to mention there must surely be a limit to how much she'll let me get away with, gullible or not."
    "Sin mencionar que seguro hay un límite de con cuánto me dejará salirme con la mía, crédula o no."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4540
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_c72e09d2:

    # "Going as far as that feels like flying a little too close to the sun."
    "Ir así de lejos sería volar muy cerca del sol."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4546
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_22b423f9:

    # h frown_side "Yeah thanks, Nozo, I know how a school works." with dissolve
    h frown_side "Seh, gracias, Nozo. Sé cómo funciona la escuela." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4548
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_412e6a6e:

    # s rolleyes "Would that you could apply that knowledge productively." with dissolve
    s rolleyes "Ojalá aplicaras ese conocimiento más productivamente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4551
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_4b8756fd:

    # h uniform_armup irritated "Whatevs. I'm just not feeling it today. Big deal!" with dissolve
    h uniform_armup irritated "Como sea. Hoy no estoy muy de buenas. ¡No es para tanto!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4553
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_01fd1d13:

    # "As the others walk to their seats, Hiroko takes a moment to stop and look my way again." with dissolve
    "Cuando las otras caminan a sus asientos, Hiroko hace una pausa para mirarme una vez más." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4554
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_e1bf9f9f:

    # "I simply smile at her, while she keeps that scowl on her face as she sits down..."
    "Yo le muestro una sonrisa, mientras ella se sienta sin quitarse el ceño fruncido."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4556
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_186d3605:

    # "And while I can't see for sure, I'm getting the impression that scowl is staying on her for the entirety of our afternoon lessons."
    "Y si bien no puedo verlo, tengo la impresión de que ese ceño permanecerá así hasta el final de las clases de la tarde."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4560
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_5d782b1c:

    # "... Hmm, maybe I could've told her I wasn't going to mess with her again today. She's probably thinking she can't let her guard down at all."
    "... Mmm, tal vez pude decirle que ya no la iba a volver a molestar hoy. Probablemente piensa que no puede bajar la guardia ni un momento."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4561
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_82a9f114:

    # "Just thinking I'll strike the very moment she tries to relax so she'll let out an embarrassing loud yawn in front of the whole class."
    "Que la atacaré en el momento en que se relaje y la haré soltar un fuerte y vergonzoso bostezo frente a toda la clase."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4564
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_98ae7314:

    # "Yeah, I'd better send her a quick, discreet text. Make sure she knows not to expect any more uh..."
    "Sí, mejor le envío un texto rápido y discreto. Le haré saber que ya no habrá más eh..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4566
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_92464c57:

    # "Wait, no, what am I doing? I stopped myself before I hit send, but I almost forgot what I had her think."
    "Espera, no, ¿qué estoy haciendo? Me detuve justo antes de presionar enviar, pero casi olvido lo que le hice creer."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4567
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_e0e89ecb:

    # "Now I kinda feel like a jerk..."
    "Ahora me siento como un cretino..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4570
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_a82124cc:

    # "So eventually the bell rings out for the end of the school day; my message left unsent on my phone."
    "Eventualmente suena la campana anunciando el final de la jornada escolar; mi mensaje quedó sin enviar en mi teléfono."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4576
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_29427510:

    # n "So I guess we'll see you on Sunday, Hiroko~" with dissolve
    n "Bueno, nos vemos el domingo, Hiroko." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4580
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_d7a45c0e:

    # n "{cps=20}All the best for... {w=0.5}{/cps}{nw}"
    n "{cps=20}Mucha suerte en... {w=0.5}{/cps}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4583
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_5a94f5ea:

    # extend "for the tournament?"
    extend "¿el torneo?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4585
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_fd2867b7:

    # "Hiroko's dark expression apparently left unchanged on her face..." with dissolve
    "La sombría expresión de Hiroko no cambió ni un poco..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4586
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_3de0049c:

    # n "Hiroko?"
    n "¿Hiroko?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4588
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_4084abc5:

    # s uniform_handup concerned "I am loathe to say it, but I fear the pressure may actually be getting to her." with dissolve
    s uniform_handup concerned "Detesto decirlo, pero me temo que la presión tal vez la esté afectando." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4589
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_3aa37680:

    # "I have to say, I've not really seen her exhibit the quiet sort of rage before."
    "He de decir que nunca la había visto exhibir ira silenciosa como esa."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4591
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_dbca5ac6:

    # n sad_closed "Yeah... I'm a little worried, to tell the truth." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Sí... Estoy algo preocupada, a decir verdad." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4592
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_e2e0781d:

    # "I thought fucking with her was gonna be a bit more fun than this. But moreso, upsetting Nozomi wasn't part of the plan..."
    "Creí que joderla sería un poco más divertido. Y para colmo, molestar a Nozomi no era parte del plan..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4593
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_2e62d9fc:

    # n sad_side "I'll send her a text; make sure she knows I'm there for her if she needs-" with dissolve
    n sad_side "Le enviaré un texto; que sepa que estaré ahí para ella si me nece-" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4598
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_c51c6e7a:

    # ks surprised "W-wait, no! Don't text her!" with dissolve
    ks surprised "¡E-espera, no! ¡No le textees!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4599
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_4adc14f6:

    # "Fuck. I just let that fall out of my mouth without thinking."
    "Carajo. Se me salió de la boca sin pensar."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4600
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_637c4d2f:

    # s concerned_right "Kyou? Is there something we can help you with?" with dissolve
    s concerned_right "¿Kyou? ¿Podemos ayudarte en algo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4602
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_789ace19:

    # "But yeah, even if she's not going to yawn anymore, getting a text from anyone right this moment seems like a really bad move." with dissolve
    "Pero sí, aunque ya no vaya a bostezar, recibir un mensaje de quien sea en este momento no creo que le vaya a sentar bien." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4603
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_1a911787:

    # ks sigh "I- I'm just saying..."
    ks sigh "S-solo digo que..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4604
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_384896a3:

    # "Not that they'd have any idea... Shit, why would they listen to anything I tell them?"
    "No es que tenga idea... Mierda, ¿por qué escucharían nada de lo que yo diga?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4606
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_6bab230d:

    # n frown "You're saying if I really cared about Hiroko I'd go to her instead of wimping out with a text." with dissolve
    n frown "Dices que, si en verdad me importara Hiroko, iría a ella en vez de quedarme aquí y solo enviarle un texto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4607
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_b8bb855a:

    # s uniform_handup rolleyes "You tried that just now and saw how that went. If you attempt to chase her there is no telling what her reaction would be." with dissolve
    s uniform_handup rolleyes "Eso mismo acabas de intentar y ya viste cómo salió. Si intentas seguirla, ¿quién sabe cuál será su reacción?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4608
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_bb2b1047:

    # n side sad_side "Hm, right. And she was pretty short with me all afternoon, now that I think of it..." with dissolve
    n side sad_side "Mm, cierto. Y tampoco estuvo muy dispuesta a hablar conmigo toda la tarde, ahora que lo pienso..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4611
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_f6338f97:

    # "Nozomi lets out an anxious-sounding sigh." with dissolve
    "Nozomi suspira con ansiedad." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4612
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_d7116bea:

    # n sad_closed "I just want her to be okay, Sayori."
    n sad_closed "Solo quiero que esté bien, Sayori."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4613
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_77f8834f:

    # s uniform_folded concerned "Of course you do. Perhaps when she has burned off some of that tension at the tennis court she'll be more amenable to our support?" with dissolve
    s uniform_folded concerned "Desde luego que sí. ¿Quizá una vez haya quemado algo de esa tensión en la cancha de tenis, se encuentre más abierta a nuestro apoyo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4614
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_44195f31:

    # n sad_side "S-so you mean..." with dissolve
    n sad_side "D-dices que..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4615
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_b7d7337c:

    # s neutral "I will fulfill my club obligations for today, then we can go see her together. She should be winding down her tennis training by then." with dissolve
    s neutral "Atenderé mis obligaciones en el club por hoy, luego iremos a verlas juntas. Estará cerca de concluir su entrenamiento de tenis para entonces." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4616
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_f925ba38:

    # n happy "Yeah. Yeah, that sounds like a plan~" with dissolve
    n happy "Sí. Sí, suena a un buen plan." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4617
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_a64b743b:

    # s smile "That it is." with dissolve
    s smile "Pues eso haremos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4620
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_37e478d8:

    # "... It kinda feels like in their discussion about what to do they forgot all about me." with dissolve
    "... Parece que en su discusión sobre qué hacer se olvidaron de mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4621
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_eaa7f895:

    # "Well, whatever. So long as Hiroko's phone doesn't go off, that's the important thing here."
    "Bueno, ¿ya qué? En tanto el teléfono de Hiroko no vibre, eso es lo que importa."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4622
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_feb59625:

    # "Now I just have to go home and wait..."
    "Ahora solo debo irme a casa y esperar..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4624
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_2f627fc3:

    # "If what happened this morning was anything to go by, Hiroko will be sure to pay me a visit no matter how miserable she might be."
    "Si las cosas siguen como esta mañana, tengo certeza de que Hiroko vendrá a visitarme, sin importar lo miserable que se sienta."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4625
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_f873b73a:

    # "Huh... Am I really starting to feel bad for Hiroko?"
    "Vaya... ¿En serio estoy empezando a sentirme mal por Hiroko?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4626
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_d5ee4044:

    # "Like, sure, maybe things got a little out of hand but it's not like I convinced her to do anything terrible today."
    "O sea, claro, puede que se me haya pasado un poco la mano, pero no es que la haya convencido de hacer nada terrible hoy."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4627
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_4fb64c2c:

    # "All she did was yawn a whole bunch, so she's probably just embarrassed by what I had her do."
    "Simplemente la hice bostezar, así que probablemente solo esté avergonzada por lo que la hice hacer."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4628
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_9ad605c2:

    # "But now she's headed to tennis practice with a clear head; maybe even more refreshed than she would have been without me."
    "Pero ahora fue a su práctica de tenis con la mente aclarada; tal vez incluso más fresca de lo que habría estado sin mí."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4629
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_6ea7addc:

    # "So yeah, Hiroko's fine. She just needs to learn a little humility so she'll start treating people with respect."
    "Entonces sí, Hiroko está bien. Solo necesita aprender algo de humildad para tratar a la gente con respeto."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4630
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_a9e4406d:

    # "I'm just teaching her a little lesson, that's all..."
    "Solo le estoy enseñando una pequeña lección. Eso es todo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4633
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_9a772891:

    # "It takes a few hours of waiting before the doorbell rings."
    "Tras algunas horas de espera, suena el timbre."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4634
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_ebb9128c:

    # "She's not trying to kick the door down this time, so I'd say she's off to a good start."
    "No está intentando derribar la puerta esta vez. Eso es un buen comienzo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4637
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_fd9fb3fd:

    # h "Hey..." with dissolve
    h "Hola..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4638
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_d98ea19f:

    # "Still, I think it's worth reminding her about the shitty way she acted last time she was here."
    "Aun así, creo que vale la pena recordarle lo mierda que se comportó la última vez que estuvo aquí."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4640
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_8f44935b:

    # ks neutral "Hey... You gonna take them off this time?" with dissolve
    ks neutral "Hola... ¿Te los vas a quitar esta vez?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4642
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_42b43932:

    # h frown "..." with dissolve
    h frown "..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4643
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_de8b8091:

    # h tennis_headhold2 confused "H-huh?! Whaddya mean?" with dissolve
    h tennis_headhold2 confused "¡¿E-eh?! ¿Qué cosas?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4644
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_974f13ae:

    # "The flash of anger in her eyes gives way to puzzlement, then realization as she notices me pointing at her shoes."
    "Un destello de enojo en sus ojos da lugar a confusión, luego comprensión al verme apuntar a sus zapatos."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4645
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_1d23c235:

    # h tennis_armup irritated vein "'COURSE I'm taking 'em off! Fuck's sake..." with vpunch
    h tennis_armup irritated vein "¡CLARO que me los voy a quitar! Puta madre..." with vpunch

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4649
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_41e9f09a:

    # "And back to anger again, as I awkwardly watch her pull off her footwear before she follows me into the house proper."
    "Y enojo otra vez. Luego se quita torpemente su calzado antes de adentrarse a la casa."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4650
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_eff98dc0:

    # ks sigh "You could've left your socks on, you know."
    ks sigh "Pudiste dejarte los calcetines puestos, ¿sabes?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4651
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_ec03d9e5:

    # h tennis_armup angry vein "Gawd, get off my case! I ain't tracking shit on your floor, okay? Jesus." with dissolve
    h tennis_armup angry vein "¡Ay, que te valga! Ni que fuera a llenar de mierda el piso. Por dios." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4652
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_71e99206:

    # ks frown "Yeah, not THIS time. After the way you behaved yesterday I have to wonder if you were raised by wolves."
    ks frown "Sí, al menos no ESTA vez. Luego de cómo te comportaste ayer, me pregunto si te criaron en un establo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4653
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_793044ec:

    # h furious vein "MOTHERFFFF..." with vpunch
    h furious vein "ME CAGO EN LA..." with vpunch

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4655
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_b8dd85e9:

    # "Hiroko cuts herself off as she starts to boil over with that all-familiar rage." with dissolve
    "Hiroko se interrumpe, hirviendo con esa tan característica ira." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4656
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_06609827:

    # h angry "Look, I ain't here to fuckin' fight you, okay? I wanna talk." with dissolve
    h angry "Mira, no vine aquí a pelear contigo, ¿de acuerdo? Quiero hablar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4657
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_e9427184:

    # "Yet curiously doesn't explode this time..."
    "Mas, curiosamente, no explota esta vez..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4658
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_9300a072:

    # ks smirk "I thought you came here to be hypnotized."
    ks smirk "Creí que habías venido aquí a ser hipnotizada."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4660
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_bb6e3eef:

    # h "H-huuuhhh..." with dissolve
    h "M-mmmm..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4661
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_521857e6:

    # "Hiroko nods slowly as she starts to anxiously rub the back of her head."
    "Hiroko asiente con ansiedad, frotándose la nuca."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4662
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_6cf8c8c8:

    # h nervous_side "H'yeah, you really got me good with this hypno crap didn't ya." with dissolve
    h nervous_side "Seh, vaya que me atrapaste con la hipno-mierda esta, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4667
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_6c7eef1e:

    # "She then unsteadily slumps down onto my couch with a groan."
    "Luego se desploma tambaleante en mi sofá con un gruñido."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4669
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_276f4347:

    # h "Didn't wanna come here for anything, but here I am. Right where you said I'd be." with dissolve
    h "No quería venir aquí para nada, pero heme aquí. Justo donde dijiste que estaría." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4671
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_9c9edd01:

    # h "Just like I've been doing everything you said I'd do all fuckin' week." with dissolve
    h "Igual que he estado haciendo todo lo que dijiste que haría toda la puta semana." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4672
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_792de239:

    # ks "Yes, Hiroko, you have. But it's like I told you: You're not doing all this JUST because I said you would."
    ks "Sí, Hiroko, es cierto. Pero como te expliqué: No lo estás haciendo SOLO porque yo dije que lo harías."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4674
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_cb9e3300:

    # ks "You might think you hate what we're doing here, but subconsciously you might actually be enjoying all of this on a deeper level." with dissolve
    ks "Tal vez creas que odias lo que estamos haciendo, pero subconscientemente quizá lo estés disfrutando a un nivel más profundo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4676
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_942d6c30:

    # h "Urgh, DON'T gimme that shit again! I KNOW all that!" with dissolve
    h "Ayy, ¡NO me vengas otra vez con esa mierda! ¡Eso YA lo sé!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4678
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_e0a711b3:

    # "She blinks sleepily, like her exertion just tired her out." with dissolve
    "Parpadea soñolienta, como si ese esfuerzo la hubiera agotado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4680
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_e8e4794a:

    # h "Mrrh... I dunno about liking this, but I've sure been thinking a lot about all this stuff. Can't get it outta my head." with dissolve
    h "Mrrh... I dunno about liking this, but I've sure been thinking a lot about all this stuff. Can't get it outta my head." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4682
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_9f1b7cf1:

    # h "Like... s-sure, maybe there's a little voice inside me saying I owe you; like I deserved to let you prank me like that." with dissolve
    h "Tal vez haya una vocecita dentro de mí diciendo que te debo una; como si me mereciera dejarte hacerme esa jugarreta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4684
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_14617593:

    # h "Or maybe you're right... Maybe it's telling me I like this, in some real fucked-up kinda way." with dissolve
    h "O tal vez tengas razón... Tal vez me está diciendo que esto me gusta, aunque suene jodido." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4686
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_852bfee5:

    # h "But come on, it don't matter what some li'l voice in my head is saying, does it?" with dissolve
    h "Pero vamos, no importa lo que diga una vocecita en mi cabeza, ¿o sí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4688
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_4109fba1:

    # h "'Cuz the BIG voice is more important!" with dissolve
    h "¡La VOCEZOTA es la que importa!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4689
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_9f0ccd29:

    # ks sigh "It's a pretty big voice, I'll give you that."
    ks sigh "Es una vocezota muy grande, no lo voy a negar."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4691
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_bae926e3:

    # h "H'yeah, and the big voice is saying I don't wanna do this shit anymore. Just like it's always been." with dissolve
    h "Seh, y la vocezota dice que ya no quiero hacer esta mierda. Y lo ha dicho desde siempre." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4692
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_b14ed87f:

    # ks frown "And do you think that's fair, Hiroko? After all I've done for you?"
    ks frown "¿Y crees tú que eso es justo, Hiroko? ¿Después de todo lo que he hecho por ti?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4693
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_3f7f1829:

    # ks "You agreed to all this when we started, remember? And I'm still holding up my end of the bargain."
    ks "Tú aceptaste todo esto cuando comenzamos, ¿recuerdas? Y yo sigo cumpliendo mi parte del trato."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4694
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_e622080a:

    # h "Y-yeah, well things change, don't they. Like how you said you wanted to do your hypno thingy at the culture fest but now you're all about this \"payback\" shit."
    h "S-sí, pues las cosas cambian, ¿no? Como cuando dijiste que querías hacer tu hipno-cosa esa en el festival cultural, pero ahora estás con esta mierda de \"desquitarte\"."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4695
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_5fe6a22c:

    # "Ignoring her, I continue to press on."
    "Ignorándola, continúo presionando."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4696
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_4e864ff8:

    # ks "By the way, how did you do on court today?"
    ks "Por cierto, ¿cómo te fue en la cancha hoy?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4698
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_8fc463d7:

    # h "It's just..." with dissolve
    h "Pues..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4700
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_63515f3c:

    # "She sighs slowly, then continues." with dissolve
    "Suspira lentamente, luego continúa..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4702
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_e1fd1888:

    # h "Like... okay, I started practice today and the second I got back on court it didn't matter how much you got under my skin." with dissolve
    h "O sea... sí, empecé a practicar hoy y el segundo que regresé a la cancha ya no importaba cuánto me habías molestado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4703
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_28833eb7:

    # h "I was totally focused on my game. Cool as ice. Like a total pro."
    h "Estaba totalmente concentrada en mi juego. Fría como el hielo. Como toda una profesional."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4705
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_9c2027d2:

    # h "And this new racket you got me kicks so much ass." with dissolve
    h "Y esta raqueta que me diste es una patea culos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4707
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_0a2daa4f:

    # h "Like, it's a li'l heavier than my old one? But I got used to it real quick and I'm gettin' so much more spin on the ball like you wouldn't believe, and..." with dissolve
    h "O sea, es un poco más ligera que la vieja. Pero me acostumbré rapidísimo, y consigo un spin en la bola que no te imaginas, y..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4709
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_e180e71d:

    # h "A-anyway, you don't care about that, it's just... I ain't saying you didn't come through for me, okay?" with dissolve
    h "C-como sea, eso a ti no te importa, es que... no niego que me ayudaste muchísimo, ¿sí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4711
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_7232ad17:

    # h "You helped me out big time; I ain't denying that." with dissolve
    h "Me ayudaste muchísimo; eso no lo niego." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4712
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_9978dace:

    # ks "Right. And you're not denying we had a mutual deal going either, are you?"
    ks "Cierto. Y tampoco niegas que teníamos un trato, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4714
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_fb533f61:

    # h "Like I said, you kinda fucked that up when you made this about payback didn't ya." with dissolve
    h "Como te dije, lo echaste un poquito a la mierda cuando hiciste eso del desquite, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4715
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_7b56f2dd:

    # ks "I made you yawn in class for a morning. So what? It's not like I did anything bad to you; just like I promised."
    ks "Te hice bostezar en clase por una mañana. ¿Y eso qué? No es como si te hubiera hecho nada malo; tal como prometí."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4717
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_cfcb90c9:

    # h "Please, just... stop, okay?" with dissolve
    h "Por favor, solo... detente, ¿sí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4718
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_ba76e358:

    # h "I know we gotta work somethin' out, but... just make it stop, I can't..."
    h "Sé que debemos llegar a algún acuerdo, pero... ya detente, no puedo..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4720
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_f9753818:

    # ks "I still want your help, Hiroko. I still want you to be my assistant for the culture fest, and that means I need to practice my skills on you." with dissolve
    ks "Aún quiero tu ayuda, Hiroko. Aún quiero que seas mi asistente para el festival cultural, y eso significa que necesito practicar mis habilidades en ti." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4722
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_9a5270ed:

    # h "{size=16}C-can't...{/size}" with dissolve
    h "{size=16}N-no puedo...{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4723
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_5fee3a54:

    # ks "And don't you think you're overreacting? I know this has to be weird for you, but I'm asking you again: Have I really done anything to hurt you?"
    ks "¿Y no crees que estás exagerando, Hiroko? Sé que debe ser raro para ti, pero en serio, preguntaré otra vez: ¿He hecho alguna vez algo para lastimarte?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4726
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_2fded262:

    # h "..."
    h "..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4727
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_d1e6cdbe:

    # ks "... Hiroko?"
    ks "... ¿Hiroko?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4728
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_493ff8d1:

    # "She's dozing off on me now? She can't be that tired after her tennis practice. And I'm sure it's nothing to do with her yawning all morning..."
    "¿Se me está quedando dormida? No puede ser que esté tan cansada por su práctica. Y sé que no tiene nada que ver con los bostezos de esta mañana..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4729
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_28921903:

    # ks "Hey, are you listening to me?"
    ks "Oye, ¿me estás escuchando?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4731
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_fe6697ad:

    # h "Mmn, yeah... listening...." with dissolve
    h "Mmn, seh... Escuchando..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4733
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_e1ed8afc:

    # "She's... hypnotized? But I wasn't even doing anything; we were just talking." with dissolve
    "Está... ¿hipnotizada? Pero ni siquiera estaba haciendo nada; solo estábamos hablando." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4734
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_a14e20cf:

    # ks neutral "Oh... That's right."
    ks neutral "Oh... Es cierto."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4735
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_c68878c5:

    # "I think aloud to myself as I suddenly realize what's happened here:"
    "Pienso en voz alta, al darme cuenta súbitamente de lo que está pasando:"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4736
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_745c3060:

    # ks "You're really getting sleepy and hypnotized just from being in my presence, aren't you?"
    ks "Estás sintiendo sueño y cayendo en trance de solo estar en mi presencia, ¿no es así?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4738
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_f623f897:

    # h "Yeah... sleepy..." with dissolve
    h "Seh... sueño..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4740
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_98b128c7:

    # ks smile "I... kinda suggested you would be when I hypnotized you yesterday, didn't I?" with dissolve
    ks smile "Te... dije que así sería cuando te hipnoticé ayer, ¿no es cierto?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4742
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_9eb50284:

    # h "Yeah..." with dissolve
    h "Seh..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4744
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_2cb9f102:

    # "Even though she was arguing that I stop hypnotizing her, she still couldn't help herself from falling back into this state." with dissolve
    "A pesar de haber estado pidiendo que dejara de hipnotizara, no pudo evitar volver a este estado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4745
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_d44fbf8a:

    # "She really has become so beholden to the hypnotic suggestions I placed into her head that following them has become so instinctual to her. So natural."
    "En verdad tiene las sugestiones hipnóticas que puse en su cabeza tan arraigadas que seguirlas se ha convertido en instinto para ella. En algo natural."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4746
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_9b81f72a:

    # "It makes me feel like I can do anything with that fascinating little mind of hers. Anything I want."
    "Me hace sentir que puedo hacer cualquier cosa con esa fascinante mentecita suya. Lo que sea que quiera."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4747
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_09e850d9:

    # "But after what she was saying I'm not so sure I should anymore."
    "Pero después de lo que dijo, ya no estoy tan seguro de si debería."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4748
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_d928bd5c:

    # "Hiroko admitted I've been a help to her, even admitted she owes me for all the shit she's put me through."
    "Hiroko admitió que la he ayudado, incluso admitió que me debe una por toda la mierda por la que me ha hecho pasar."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4749
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_9fb3521d:

    # "She sounded almost... reasonable?"
    "Sonó casi... ¿razonable?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4750
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_66ee74af:

    # "So maybe it's time I stopped playing games and heard her out some more."
    "Entonces, tal vez sea hora de dejar de jugar y escucharla un poco más."
    
