    # h angry "What, you ain't gonna bring it up again? Fine, then I'm gonna." with dissolve
    h angry "¿Qué, no quieres hablar de eso? Bueno, pues lo voy a hacer yo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4995
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_ab851540:

    # h frown "I'm sorry I punched you in the face." with dissolve
    h frown "Siento haberte golpeado en la cara." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4996
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_edb0b286:

    # h frown_side "I know you think it's cuz' I hate you, and I do. But it was just a reflex thing; you didn't give me a choice." with dissolve
    h frown_side "Sé que crees que fue porque te odio, y pues sí te odio. Pero solo fue un reflejo; no me diste elección." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4997
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_8298201d:

    # h sad_side "It was so freaky what you were doing wasn't it? I ain't ever laughed like that, and all you had to do was tickle my hand a li'l bit?" with dissolve
    h sad_side "Lo que estabas haciendo era bastante aterrador, ¿no? Nunca me había reído así, ¿y solo bastaba con que me hicieras cosquillas en la mano?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4998
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_4104f2fa:

    # h tennis_headhold "I didn't get how that could happen. Didn't get it at all." with dissolve
    h tennis_headhold "No entendía cómo podía pasar eso. De verdad no entendía." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:4999
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_06d25caa:

    # h sad "All I knew was I needed you to stop, and you didn't... you didn't stop." with dissolve
    h sad "Solo sabía que necesitaba que pararas, y no parabas... no parabas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5000
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_1f881033:

    # ks neutral "..."
    ks neutral "..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5001
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_695d04ac:

    # h nervous "What else was I supposed to do?" with dissolve
    h nervous "¿Qué otra cosa se suponía que hiciera?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5002
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_3e32bd14:

    # "With a sigh, I turn back around to be met with... with the kind of sincere expression I've never seen on her face before."
    "Con un suspiro, me doy nuevamente la vuelta para encontrarme con... con la clase de expresión sincera que nunca antes había visto en su rostro."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5003
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_eb8c2468:

    # ks sigh "It's... it was just tickling, Hiroko. You didn't need to worry about it."
    ks sigh "Solo... solo eran cosquillas, Hiroko. No tenías por qué preocuparte."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5004
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_ec4bacd1:

    # h furious "Y-YOU didn't need to worry about it! That's why you went too fuckin' far!" with dissolve
    h furious "¡T-TÚ no tenías por qué preocuparte! ¡Por eso seguiste por cuanto te dio la jodida gana!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5005
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_2bde13eb:

    # h confused "I couldn't breathe, but you didn't care, did you? You were too busy having fun \"just tickling\" me." with dissolve
    h confused "No podía respirar, pero a ti no te importó, ¿verdad? Estabas muy ocupado divirtiéndote haciéndome \"solo cosquillas\"." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5006
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_9bcc0c3e:

    # h pain "That's why you let me get tortured all day until I was kicking your damn door! You didn't care!" with dissolve
    h pain "¡Por eso me dejaste sufrir todo el día hasta que llegué a patearte la maldita puerta! ¡No te importó!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5007
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_e008fd4a:

    # ks frown "You didn't need to kick it."
    ks frown "No tenías por qué patearla."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5008
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_33a4b867:

    # h confused "Didn't I? How else were you gonna hear me out?" with dissolve
    h confused "¿Ah, no? ¿Y de qué otra forma me ibas a escuchar?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5009
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_b337bc6f:

    # h tennis frown "Every time you've done this shit, I've had to beg and plead an' just, like... hope you'll stop because you dunno when to stop." with dissolve
    h tennis frown "Cada vez que has hecho esta mierda, tuve que rogarte y suplicarte y, pues... rezar por que te detuvieras porque no sabes cuándo parar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5010
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_6eb60a48:

    # h sleeptalk "And... an' that's the problem with you, ain't it." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "Y... y ese es el problema contigo, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5011
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_88c73325:

    # h nervous "You dunno when to stop..." with dissolve
    h nervous "No sabes cuándo parar..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5012
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_0fa53c61:

    # "Man. There sure is a part of me that wants to push back on that. Like she's any better about knowing when to quit."
    "Caray. Una parte de mí en serio quiere protestar contra eso. Como si ella tuviera muy buen juicio de cuándo pisar el freno."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5013
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_afa8bc82:

    # "All the times she's given me shit and never backed off. The screaming match she had with her tennis partner that drove her away..."
    "Todas esas veces en las que me ha hecho pasar por tanta mierda sin dar ni un paso atrás. El duelo de gritos que tuvo con su compañera de tenis que terminó alejándola..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5014
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_a7f2cbec:

    # "... But nothing good's going to come from bringing that up now, is there?"
    "... Pero mencionar eso ahora no traerá nada bueno, ¿o sí?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5015
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_71b9b9a3:

    # ks sad "I guess I don't. And I'm sorry for that."
    ks sad "Supongo que es cierto. Y me disculpo por eso."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5016
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_a3bf69ab:

    # ks "But I still don't get it. Everything I read about hypnosis said that a subject always had the ability to reject any suggestion made to them, no matter how deep they were."
    ks "Pero aun así no lo entiendo. Todo lo que leí sobre hipnosis decía que un sujeto siempre tiene la habilidad de rechazar una sugestión, sin importar lo profundo que se encuentre."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5017
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_e108e517:

    # ks "It shouldn't have mattered much if I was messing with you or not. Hypnosis isn't some dark art or anything like that."
    ks "No debería importar si intentaba divertirme a tus expensas o no. La hipnosis no es una especie de arte oscuro ni nada parecido."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5018
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_f5b57081:

    # h tennis_headhold sleeptalk "Well... maybe you didn't read enough, huh." with dissolve
    h tennis_headhold sleeptalk "Pues... tal vez no leíste suficiente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5019
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_b9b321d2:

    # ks sigh "I really was too into getting my own back to think about what all this was doing to you."
    ks sigh "De verdad me enfoqué tanto en desquitarme que no pensé en lo que esto te estaba haciendo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5020
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_23f38f9e:

    # h sad_side "Yeah... that about sums it up, don't it." with dissolve
    h sad_side "Sí... supongo que eso lo resume bien, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5021
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_9da6b47e:

    # "So we stand there, silently, as a question unspoken looms between us."
    "Y entonces nos quedamos aquí parados, en silencio, y una pregunta sin pronunciar yace en el aire."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5022
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_39082f46:

    # "\"What happens now?\""
    "\"¿Qué pasará ahora?\""

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5024
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_32a9120b:

    # "But eventually, Hiroko lets out a sigh before looking to me once more." with dissolve
    "Pero eventualmente, Hiroko suelta un suspiro, para después voltear a verme una vez más." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5025
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_5492072a:

    # h tennis neutral "Look, I gotta get out of here. Still got a tourney to win." with dissolve
    h tennis neutral "Mira, me tengo que ir de aquí. Aún tengo un torneo que ganar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5026
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_2865cdc2:

    # h sleep "We'll... we'll pick this up later. Okay?" with dissolve
    h sleep "Lo... lo discutimos después. ¿Está bien?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5027
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_11ac04ff:

    # ks neutral "... Sure."
    ks neutral "... Claro."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5030
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_d36c2bdc:

    # "So I see her out, and I'm left thinking about everything that's gone on between us."
    "Luego ella se va, y yo me quedo pensando en todo lo que ha sucedido entre nosotros."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5033
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_c00905e3:

    # "It might have been fun to mess with her the way I did, but... I know I pushed her too far."
    "Puede que haya sido divertido jugar con ella así, pero... sé que la empujé demasiado lejos."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5034
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_248de123:

    # "But why was it so... so easy? My first time hypnotizing someone, and it felt like I could convince her of anything."
    "Pero ¿por qué fue tan... tan fácil? Es la primera vez que hipnotizo a alguien, y parecía que podía convencerla de lo que fuera."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5037
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_9e1e05e2:

    # "And all it took was a few words and this thing? Maybe Hiroko was right."
    "¿Y solo hicieron falta unas cuantas palabras y esta cosa? Tal vez Hiroko tenía razón."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5038
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_2d52b054:

    # "Maybe I didn't read enough."
    "Tal vez no leí suficiente."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5040
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_fb69bfcc:

    # "Still. Even with all that, she wants to talk to me again. At least, if I haven't fucked up her chances at that tournament."
    "Sin embargo, incluso después de todo eso, quiere volver a hablar conmigo. Eso si es que no eché a la mierda sus oportunidades en ese torneo, claro."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5041
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_56730793:

    # "I have no idea how she'll do over there. All that mental conditioning I gave her; was that all for nothing now?"
    "No tengo idea de cómo le irá allá. Todo el acondicionamiento mental que le di; ¿ahora todo eso fue para nada?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5042
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_88dcd90b:

    # "... I should go to see her, at the tournament."
    "... Debería ir a verla, en el torneo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:5045
translate spanish Hiroko_Trickster_SealTheDeal_8291c408:

    # "I'll find out for myself..."
    "Lo averiguaré con mis propios ojos..."

