# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2384
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_2ac16b71:

    # "It's Friday, and I'm walking to school with some really high hopes for tonight."
    "Es viernes, y yo camino a la escuela con altas expectativas para esta noche."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2387
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_4eca9535:

    # "When people talk about their plans for the start of the weekend, I'd always feel left out."
    "Cuando la gente habla de sus planes para empezar el fin de semana, yo siempre me siento excluido."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2388
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_22c298b7:

    # "It's not like I've had anything going on with me for years."
    "Al fin y al cabo, no he tenido nada interesante qué hacer en años."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2389
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_dfe66f76:

    # "Or like anyone would bother to ask."
    "Y tampoco es que nadie se molestara en preguntarme."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2391
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_5238c536:

    # "But this time..." with dissolve
    "Pero esta vez..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2394
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_2b87cd7b:

    # h "Man, wish this school day would go to hell already." with dissolve
    h "Caray, quisiera que este día de escuela ya se fuera al diablo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2395
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_15cf4409:

    # "This time the start of my weekend is going to be very interesting indeed."
    "Esta vez el inicio del fin de semana será muy interesante."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2397
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_17131bb7:

    # n "Mhm, I know what you mean. Are you all set for the weekend?" with dissolve
    n "Mjm, te entiendo. ¿Todas listas para el fin de semana?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2398
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_2734ab91:

    # "Especially if the best girl in school has anything to say about it."
    "Todo gracias a la mejor chica de toda la escuela."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2399
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_70e2fae5:

    # h neutral_side "H'yeah, I'd better be. I've trained all year for this." with dissolve
    h neutral_side "Seh, más me vale. Entrené todo el año para esto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2400
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_097f0c8b:

    # h angry_side "I just wanna get out there an' show everyone what I've got." with dissolve
    h angry_side "Solo quiero ir allá afuera mostrarles a todos lo que tengo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2401
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_91d7839f:

    # h uniform_armup "An' you all BETTER be ready for it!" with dissolve
    h uniform_armup "¡Así que váyanse PREPARANDO!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2402
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_c3f54925:

    # n happy "Mhmhmhm~" with dissolve
    n happy "Jejejeje." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2403
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_107445ca:

    # n smile "Yeah. I'm looking forward to it." with dissolve
    n smile "Sí. No puedo esperar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2404
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_a48ed6bd:

    # "Still wish she'd give me a heads up on what she's planning, though."
    "Aun así quisiera que me contara lo que está planeando."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2410
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_d19fafac:

    # "But she doesn't reply to my texts I send during lunchbreak, as she spends the hour with her friends."
    "Pero no responde a los textos que le envío durante el almuerzo, pues pasa la hora con sus amigas."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2411
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_f1502aea:

    # "Yeah, figures I wouldn't get anything out of her."
    "Sí, me imaginaba que no podría sacarle nada."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2414
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_acd8133b:

    # "It just makes me more excited to find out as the school day slowly, but uneventfully draws to a close."
    "Solo hace que me emocione más por averiguarlo conforme la jornada escolar llega lenta y monótonamente a su fin."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2416
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_1edd9095:

    # "So I head home, trying not to look in too much of a hurry."
    "Así que me dirijo a casa, intentando no lucir muy apresurado."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2418
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_bb184561:

    # "Just like before, she doesn't keep me waiting."
    "Al igual que antes, no me deja esperando."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2421
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_62d2c3a1:

    # n "H-hi..."
    n "Ho-hola..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2424
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_63553a3d:

    # "And as she steps inside and struggles out of her shoes, I smile as I produce the penlight from my pocket before handing it to her."
    "Y mientras ella entra y se quita los zapatos entre traspiés, yo le sonrío y saco la linterna de mi bolsillo para dársela."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2425
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_9d2d59d6:

    # ks smile "So, are you going to tell me what you plan to do with this thing?"
    ks smile "Entonces, ¿ya vas a decirme qué planeas hacer con esta cosa?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2432
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_2bc4718d:

    # "She takes it and moves past me into the living room."
    "Ella la toma y me rodea camino a la sala."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2433
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_286c6c09:

    # "There's no answer from her. All she has for me is that impish little smile on her lips to keep me in suspense before she finally speaks."
    "No me da una respuesta. Lo único que me ofrece es esa sonrisita traviesa en sus labios para mantenerme en suspenso hasta que finalmente habla."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2434
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_fb0337cd:

    # n smile "Take a seat, Kyou." with dissolve
    n smile "Toma asiento, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2438
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_27851b91:

    # "When I sit, I look up to find her already standing over me, penlight raised."
    "Cuando me siento, miro arriba y encuentro a Nozomi ya de pie frente a mí, con la linterna en el aire."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2439
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_8af38f9a:

    # ks smile "Come on, you gotta tell me what you're going to do with that thing."
    ks smile "Vamos, tienes que decirme lo que vas a hacer con esa cosa."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2442
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_afd4e3f3:

    # n "Ahahaha~" with dissolve
    n "Ajajaja." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2443
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_aebdf0b4:

    # "She's shaking her head at me? What gives?"
    "¿Me sacude la cabeza? ¿Qué pasa?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2445
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_68e1e506:

    # n "Kyou... do you trust me?" with dissolve
    n "Kyou... ¿confías en mí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2446
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_26ee3ff5:

    # "She asks me with that tone, and I'm not sure what to make of it."
    "Me pregunta con ese tono, y no estoy seguro de qué pensar."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2447
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_1b287dd3:

    # "But, well, I guess that was never in any doubt."
    "Pero, bueno, supongo que eso nunca estuvo en duda."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2448
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_7d0e5038:

    # ks confused "Of course. But..."
    ks confused "Por supuesto. Pero..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2453
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_5fcdf1e9:

    # n "Good. Now just relax and don't worry about a thing."
    n "Bien. Ahora solo relájate y no te preocupes por nada."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2455
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_8a127567:

    # "She's already starting?! But I..."
    "¡¿Ya está empezando?! Pero..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2447
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_2465735b:

    # n "Let yourself sink into the couch and focus all your attention on this light."
    n "Deja que tu cuerpo se huna en el sofá y enfoca toda tu atención en esta luz."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2459
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_68e6e731:

    # "Wow, that light really is something. My eyes almost move on their own while she..."
    "Guau, esa luz es poderosa. Mis ojos casi se mueven por sí solos mientras..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2463
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_f6a7dd02:

    # "... Wait, what was I doing? Did something move?"
    "... Espera, ¿qué estaba haciendo? ¿Algo se movió?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2465
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_e94769dc:

    # n "... Detective?"
    n "... ¿Detective?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2466
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_ed97ea63:

    # ks confused "Hm? I..."
    ks confused "¿Mm? Eh..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2467
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_b379e42f:

    # "... Oh. That's right."
    "... Oh. Es cierto."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2471
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_d2a768e1:

    # "I'm supposed to be dealing with this perp we just brought in for questioning."
    "Se supone que me encargue de esta granuja que acabamos de traer para interrogarla."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2461
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_f2730330:

    # k "You're in a whole heap of trouble, missy."
    k "Estás metida en muchos problemas, muchachita."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2481
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_00dd889a:

    # "I glare at her, and the young woman rigidly folds her arms as she stiffens under my gaze." with dissolve
    "Le doy una mirada, y la joven se cruza rígidamente de brazos, poniéndose tensa frente a mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2482
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_c99799ea:

    # n "Oh, am I now?"
    n "Oh, ¿de veras?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2465
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_88ba96e4:

    # k "Do you have anything to say for yourself?"
    k "¿Tienes algo que decir en tu defensa?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2486
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_78e78fb8:

    # n "Hmph, what is there to say? I don't even know what I'm in here for!" with dissolve
    n "Mmmf, ¿qué hay que decir? ¡Ni siquiera sé para qué estoy aquí!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2487
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_260e0645:

    # "I can feel my eyebrow twitch irritatedly all on it's own. Is she for real?"
    "Puedo sentir mis cejas retorcerse de irritación por sí solas. ¿Es en serio?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2469
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_2adaf41b:

    # k "Don't you dare play dumb with me! You know EXACTLY what you've done!"
    k "¡No te hagas la tonta! ¡Sabes EXACTAMENTE lo que hiciste!"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2471
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_38e57741:

    # k "And by god, I swear you're going down for this if it's the last thing I fucking do!" with dissolve
    k "¡Y por juro por Dios caerás por esto aunque sea lo último que haga en mi puta vida!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2495
translate spanish Day5_Switch_Safe_1ccb1fa7:

    # n "And what crime have I supposedly commited, \"Detective\"?" with dissolve
    n "¿Y qué crimen presuntamente cometí, \"detective\"?" with dissolve

