    n neutral_left "¿Ya, em... sabes lo que vas a hacer esta noche?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2776
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_616790f5:

    # ks smile "Yeah. We'll start whenever you're ready."
    ks smile "Sí. Comenzamos cuando estés lista."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2780
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_eac0d503:

    # "Nozomi nods as she wastes no time in slipping off her shoes and following me straight to the living room before making a beeline for the couch."
    "Nozomi asiente y, sin perder tiempo, se quita los zapatos y me sigue directo a la sala, para luego ir en línea recta al sofá."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2784
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_2f691108:

    # ks smile "Okay, so what I was thinking was, once you're under I'll..."
    ks smile "Bien, pues se me ocurrió que, una vez estés en trance, te..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2785
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_af2ce8b6:

    # "I trail off in my explanation as Nozomi meekly holds her hand up."
    "Me detengo a media explicación al ver a Nozomi alzar dócilmente la mano."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2786
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_e84881de:

    # n "No, it's alright. You don't have to explain it to me. Just do what you had in mind."
    n "No, descuida. No tienes que explicármelo. Solo haz lo que tenías en mente."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2787
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_53561703:

    # ks confused "Huh, what?"
    ks confused "Eh, ¿qué?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2788
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_65c9c2c2:

    # "The hell does she mean I don't have to explain it? Wasn't she adamant that I did?"
    "¿Qué diablos quiere decir con que no tengo que explicarlo? ¿No estaba muy firme con eso?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2789
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_5666c39f:

    # ks "... You're sure?"
    ks "... ¿Segura?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2790
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_bb2e71cf:

    # "But now she's totally fine with me just doing whatever?"
    "Pero ¿ahora le parece bien que yo haga lo que sea?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2791
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_e7feecdd:

    # n "Very sure. Go ahead, Kyou."
    n "Muy segura. Adelante, Kyou."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2792
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_0107da92:

    # "I'm really having a hard time figuring her out, but..."
    "De verdad me está costando mucho entenderla, pero..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2793
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_56df2199:

    # ks smile "Alright. Then it's [hypno3!l], Nozomi."
    ks smile "Muy bien. Entonces es [hypno3!l!t], Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2796
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_ee667d7a:

    # "If this is how she wants it, then am I really going to complain?" with dissolve
    "Si así es como lo quiere, ¿quién soy yo para quejarme?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2797
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_fb08d45f:

    # ks neutral "That's right, Nozomi. Just feeling yourself sink back into this relaxing, wonderful state of trance."
    ks neutral "Eso es, Nozomi. De regreso a este relajante y maravilloso estado de trance."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2799
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_ce4775bf:

    # "And by the way she just dropped like a rock again, it feels like she really wants it..."
    "Y por la forma en la que volvió a caer como tronco, parece que de verdad lo quiere..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2800
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_617468bc:

    # ks "Sinking all the way back. Ready to listen. Ready to accept more of my suggestions and, just for a while, awaken to a new reality."
    ks "Completamente de regreso. Lista para escuchar. Lista para aceptar más de mis sugestiones y, solo por un rato, despertar en una nueva realidad."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2801
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_f8033e07:

    # ks "Right, Nozomi?"
    ks "¿Cierto, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2803
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_26d07915:

    # n "Right..." with dissolve
    n "Cierto..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2805
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_46c15e1d:

    # "So now I gotta enact this plan she doesn't know about and hope she likes what I've come up with." with dissolve
    "Y ahora debo poner en marcha este plan del que no sabe nada y esperar que le guste lo que se me ocurrió." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2806
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_5ec20316:

    # ks "That's exactly right. Now listen carefully..."
    ks "Así es. Ahora escucha con cuidado..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2807
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_03b5b2e1:

    # "No pressure."
    "Sin presiones."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2808
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_6cef4897:

    # ks "I want you to think back to when we first met in this room three days ago and sat down on this very couch, waiting to be hypnotized."
    ks "Quiero que pienses en la primera vez que nos reunimos en esta sala hace tres días y te sentaste en este sofá, esperando ser hipnotizada."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2809
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_b2a2a353:

    # ks "Because when I next wake you, you're going to find yourself transported back to that moment in time."
    ks "Porque la próxima vez que te despierte, te habrás transportado de vuelta a ese instante del tiempo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2810
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_65ff3fca:

    # ks "So you will not be able to recall anything we have done together since."
    ks "Por lo que no podrás recordar nada de lo que hemos hecho juntos desde entonces."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2811
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_8644f74d:

    # ks "As far as you know, we've just come back from the coffee shop and I'm about to hypnotize you for the very first time."
    ks "En lo que a ti concierne, acabamos de venir desde la cafetería y estoy por hipnotizarte por primera vez."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2812
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_419fb8da:

    # ks "Do you understand, Nozomi?"
    ks "¿Comprendes, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2814
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_f5ce299b:

    # n "Yes..." with dissolve
    n "Sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2816
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_c2f851ab:

    # ks "That's good. However, something will be different. Because you really have been hypnotized, and you're going to respond to another hypnotic trigger for the rest of the evening." with dissolve
    ks "Muy bien. No obstante, algo diferente va a pasar. Porque en realidad sí has sido hipnotizada, y vas a responder a otro anclaje hipnótico por el resto de la velada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2817
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_7e7be609:

    # "As I speak those words, a few thoughts cross my mind that I'm surprised I hadn't considered before now..."
    "Mientras pronuncio esas palabras, se me cruzan un par de pensamientos por la mente que me sorprende no haber considerado hasta ahora..."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2818
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_a69e7bfd:

    # ks "Whenever I tell you I'm \"taking initiative\" you will, for a few moments, experience a sleepy sensation as you find yourself obeying whatever suggestion I just gave to you."
    ks "Cada vez que te diga que estoy \"tomando iniciativa\", experimentarás, por unos momentos, una sensación soñolienta y obedecerás cualquier sugestión que recién te haya dado."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2819
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_d0b15959:

    # "Does this technically count as taking more than one turn if I'm gonna be trancing her a bunch of times?"
    "¿Cuenta esto técnicamente como tomar más de un turno si voy a ponerla en trance varias veces?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2820
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_70456b64:

    # ks "The more you experience this sensation, the more you will come to realize that you were hypnotized before you even set foot in my house."
    ks "Entre más experimentes esta sensación, más te darás cuenta de que fuiste hipnotizada antes de siquiera poner un pie en mi casa."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2821
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_97be092c:

    # "And isn't what I'm putting in her hypnotized head a little complicated? I'm really expecting her to follow along with all of this?"
    "¿Y no es un poco complicado lo que estoy poniendo en su cabeza? ¿De verdad espero que siga el hilo con todo?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2822
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_d9e919ec:

    # ks "Do you understand everything I've told you, Nozomi?"
    ks "¿Comprendes todo lo que te he dicho, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2823
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_65aad767:

    # "Well. Guess it's too late to think of a saner plan now."
    "Bueno. Supongo que es muy tarde para pensar en un plan más sensato."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2825
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_56d76425:

    # n "Yes... I understand..." with dissolve
    n "Sí... comprendo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2826
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_09e53ac7:

    # "Although somehow, I just know this isn't going to make her mad at me."
    "Aunque de alguna forma, sé que esto no va a hacer que se moleste conmigo."

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2828
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_9c584b76:

    # ks "Perfect. And one more thing. The moment you leave the house or I say \"Back to reality\", you will immediately lose every suggestion I've made to you tonight." with dissolve
    ks "Perfecto. Y una cosa más. En el momento en que salgas de mi casa o yo diga \"De vuelta a la realidad\", perderás automáticamente cada sugestión que te haya hecho esta noche." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2829
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_31f953da:

    # ks "You will recall everything that has happened and these suggestions will no longer have any effect on you. Okay, Nozomi?"
    ks "Recordarás todo lo que ha pasado y estas sugestiones ya no tendrán ningún efecto sobre ti. ¿Muy bien, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2831
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_da655bad:

    # n "Okay..." with dissolve
    n "Bien..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2833
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_250b77e9:

    # ks "That's great. Now, waking up in three." with dissolve
    ks "Grandioso. Ahora despierta a las tres." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 5.rpy:2834
translate spanish Day5_Switch_UnSafe_2a6a8f5c:

    # ks "One, two... three."
    ks "Uno, dos... tres."

